g/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_burger-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\n[Personal](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n[Business](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/business-banking)\n\n[Corporate](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/corporate-banking)\n\n[Investment Banking](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/investment-banking)\n\n[Islamic](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/islamic-banking)\n\n[Private](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/private)\n\n[About FAB](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/about-fab)\n\n[Subsidiaries](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/subsidiaries)\n\n[Insights](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/insights)\n\nInternational\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal \"First Abu Dhabi Bank home page\")\n\n![Search](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/banner/cashback-header-en.jpg?h=530&iar=0&w=1440&hash=3097B3D770A40F963F59FBC1594A4110)\n\n![Two FAB Cashback Credit Cards](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/cashback-card-mockup.png?h=594&iar=0&w=848&hash=53E368A665898134E0BF76060059344B)\n\n# FAB Cashback Credit Card\n\nBoost your wallet with up to  1,000 monthly.\n\nEarn up to 5% cashback on fashion, dining and groceries.\n\n[Apply now](https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=E23CD4F2-47FF-46A7-9EED-E1400C5812E5&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=none&utm_keyword=not%20provided&utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fcashback-credit-card&tst_id=null#apply-now \"\")\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2026/cashback-credit-card-amazon-gift-card-offer/conventional-offer-tile-spring-madness.jpg?h=702&iar=0&w=818&hash=C474618D757F3C282FDBE78B912A6AE8)\n\nApply for a new FAB Cashback Credit Card by 15 May 2026 and you’ll get an Amazon Gift Card worth up to  1,000.\n\n- Apply for your new card by 15 May 2026.\n- Spend  10,000 to receive a  1,000 Amazon Gift Card or  5,000 to receive a  500 Amazon Gift Card within 30 days of when your card is issued.\n- Benefit from a first year fee waiver.\n\n[Terms and Conditions Apply.](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2026/cashback-credit-card-amazon-gift-card-offer/cashback-credit-card-amazon-gift-card-offer_en.pdf?view=1)\n\n[Apply now\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card#get-your-card \"\")\n\n## Get great discounts, cashback and exciting benefits.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/enjoy-5pc-cashback.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=05662E82B89F35A081DC8AF88767BFD4)\n\n### Enjoy 5% cashback on food and fashion\n\nReceive 5% cashback on fashion shopping and dining out.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/get-cashback-on-groceries.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=78F02BF0CF22043B4611A1D4D753BD21)\n\n### Get 5% cashback on groceries and Carrefour online discounts\n\nBenefit from 5% cashback on groceries, and  40 off Carrefour online.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/cashback-on-international-spend.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=E0A853FABCC07841533C478DCA1113DB)\n\n### Earn 3% cashback on international spends\n\nEarn 3% cashback on international spends and FREE worldwide airport lounge access.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/cashback-on-other-spend.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=2E7C700A0303D005517FFFAF81C9965B)\n\n### Cashback on all your other spending\n\nMore for you with 1% cashback on all your other spending.\n\n## Get great discounts, cashback and exciting benefits.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/enjoy-5pc-cashback.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=05662E82B89F35A081DC8AF88767BFD4)\n\n### Enjoy 5% cashback on food and fashion\n\nReceive 5% cashback on fashion shopping and dining out.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/get-cashback-on-groceries.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=78F02BF0CF22043B4611A1D4D753BD21)\n\n### Get 5% cashback on groceries and Carrefour online discounts\n\nBenefit from 5% cashback on groceries, and  40 off Carrefour online.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/cashback-on-international-spend.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=E0A853FABCC07841533C478DCA1113DB)\n\n### Earn 3% cashback on international spends\n\nEarn 3% cashback on international spends and FREE worldwide airport lounge access.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/cashback-on-other-spend.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=2E7C700A0303D005517FFFAF81C9965B)\n\n### Cashback on all your other spending\n\nMore for you with 1% cashback on all your other spending.\n\n##  5,000\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n##  300\n\nAnnual Fee\n\n##  5,000\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n##  300\n\nAnnual Fee\n\n## Get great cashback whenever you spend.\n\n| What you spend on | The cashback you get | FAB Rewards earned | Monthly Cap |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Supermarket | 5% | 17 FAB Rewards /  1 Spend |  150 |\n| Fashion | 5% | 17 FAB Rewards /  1 Spend |  150 |\n| Dining | 5% | 17 FAB Rewards /  1 Spend |  150 |\n| All other spending excluding select categories | 1% | 3.5 FAB Rewards /  1 Spend | - |\n| Select categories | 0.15% | 0.5 FAB Rewards /  1 Spend | - |\n| Cashback for non-AED spending | 3% | 10 FAB Rewards /  1 Spend | - |\n| Overall Cap on cashback | Rewards will be granted up to  1,000 or until eligible spends reach the credit limit, <br>whichever comes first. |\n\n### It’s good to know:\n\n- There is a minimum spend criteria of  3,000 in the previous month to be eligible to earn FAB Rewards.\n- To learn more about select categories and all other spending, please read the below Terms & Conditions PDF.\n- Cashback will be processed in equivalent FAB Rewards, redeemable instantly on the FAB Mobile app.\n\n## Lifestyle\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/1.svg?iar=0&hash=8157A2BDD7580DE3A88FC4807CF5B63A)\n\n40% off Talabat orders\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/3.svg?iar=0&hash=C0E3BDDD046C1FAFD245CAD871251FD0)\n\nMovie tickets for  20\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/2.svg?iar=0&hash=E18468F856DDB3C60CE046DEC3B550B5)\n\nCarrefour online discounts\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n40% off Talabat orders\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy great restaurant deals! Get 40% off orders on the Talabat app with up to  40 off each order, four times a month with a minimum order of  100. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/pdf/talabat-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nHead to the cinema with tickets for  20\n\n\n\n\n\nWatch all the latest movies with two movie tickets a month for  20 at Reel Cinemas, Cine Royal and Star Cinemas. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/lifestyle/cinema-en.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nCarrefour online discounts\n\n\n\n\n\n 40 off Carrefour online when you spend a minimum of  250 once every month. [Learn more](https://www.carrefouruae.com/mafuae/en/n/c/clp_mastercard-world-worldelite)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree coffee with Costa\n\n\n\n\n\nGrab a free coffee with Costa! Get up to 2 Costa coffees at Dubai Airport plus another 2 items (from a selected list). [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/194249/costa-coffee-complimentary-food-drink/0/4007/options/sortBy/popularity/category/1021/)\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nCashback on other spending and shopping\n\n\n\n\n\nYou don’t need to spend on groceries alone to save! Earn 1% extra cashback on all your other spending, save with every purchase. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/fab-cashback-creditcard-tnc-en-01082024.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nEnjoy 10% off incredible fashion with Farfetch\n\n\n\n\n\nThis one’s for the trendsetters and the fashion fans. Get 10% off Farfetch.com when you spend a minimum of USD 300. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/shopping/product/163188/farfetch-discount/0/4007/options/cardType/3/)\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n15% off Bicester Village Shopping Collection\n\n\n\n\n\nYou can also enjoy 15% off when you shop with the Bicester Village Shopping Collection (Applicable on shopping packages, chauffer drive experiences and shopping express). [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/shopping/product/163190/bicester-village-shopping-collection/0/4007/options/cardType/3/)\\*\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [priceless.com](https://www.priceless.com/benefits-mea) for the latest updates.\n\n## Travel\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/4.svg?iar=0&hash=80BA770C684B8E6C8060FC65354D79A1)\n\n40% off MakeMyTrip bookings\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/5.svg?iar=0&hash=445AEDB431DAFFE0871D58B6A5A346B2)\n\nFree airport lounge access and airport transfers\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/6.svg?iar=0&hash=7FF3DCC0804E0EC28DC9AE56DB01514C)\n\nCashback on travel spends\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n40% off MakeMyTrip bookings\n\n\n\n\n\nSave big with exclusive travel deals, get up to 40% off flights and hotel bookings through MakeMyTrip. You will also receive a 10% bonus in your MMT wallet (up to  100) for each traveller, with a maximum of five people per booking. Enjoy a 20% discount on hotel bookings, up to  300. You’ll also get a 20% bonus in your MMT wallet, up to  300, when you spend at least  300. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/travel/makemytrip-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree worldwide airport lounge access\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy free worldwide airport lounge access for you and your plus one! Relax with up to 8 free lounge visits per year, while your plus one receives 6 complimentary visits. Elevate your travel experience with these exclusive lounge benefits. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/168080/world-mastercard-lounge-program-dp/0/4007/options/category/509/location/19588/cardType/3/)\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nSave more with 3% cashback on spending when travelling\n\n\n\n\n\nSave more with 3% cashback on travel and enjoy a variety of exclusive travel offers. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/fab-cashback-creditcard-tnc-en-01082024.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree airport transfers\n\n\n\n\n\nBenefit from hassle-free transportation with 1 free airport transfer. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/195122/complimentary-airport-transfers-with-careem/0/4007/options/sortBy/popularity/category/1021/)\\*\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [priceless.com](https://www.priceless.com/benefits-mea) for the latest updates.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/overview/cards-images/fab-cashback-credit-card-2.png?iar=0&hash=3B44ACA25D612D307F7763139276AD71)\n\n## Apply now for a FAB Cashback Credit Card\n\nReady to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n **5,000**\n\n![Percentage Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/icon-percentage)\n\nReady to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.\n\n[Apply now](https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=E23CD4F2-47FF-46A7-9EED-E1400C5812E5&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=none&utm_keyword=not%20provided&utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fcashback-credit-card&tst_id=null#apply-now \"\")\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2025/mclaren-f1-cards-offer/10-card-pdp-promo-tile-mclaren-f1.jpg?h=832&iar=0&w=1024&hash=C9567B08FE8C6813EBAD068966F16FEA)\n\nAs the Official Race Partner of the McLaren F1 Team, FAB is bringing the thrill of the track to your wallet.\n\nFor a limited time, your card will transform with exclusive McLaren F1 artwork.\n\nPlus, subscribe to our McLaren Racing Mastercard Pass and enjoy exclusive fan content and freebies, and a chance to win a trip to the McLaren Technology Centre in the UK and much more.\n\n[Learn more\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/promotions/mclaren-f1-cards-offer \"\")\n\n## How to easily apply for your credit card online\n\nWatch this short video and see how you can apply for a FAB credit card online in just a few minutes.\n\nHow to Apply Online for a FAB Credit Card\\_EN from First Abu Dhabi Bank on Vimeo\n\n![video thumbnail](https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/2007623580-1ac9340085989191c4046e707c893dba9ffecac73264f60c91c1147d38d981a0-d?mw=80&q=85)\n\nPlaying in picture-in-picture\n\nPlay\n\n00:00\n\n01:33\n\nSettings\n\nQualityAuto\n\nPicture-in-PictureFullscreen\n\n;\n\n## Make the most of your credit card with FAB's fantastic offers\n\n[See all offers\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers \"\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/the-green-planet/green-planet-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=F3E4C17F9CC3E76374BDD41CB9FEDB5D)\\\\\n\\\\\nThe Green Planet\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 20% discount on day-passes\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/the-green-planet-fab \"The Green Planet\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/dubai-parks-resorts/dpr-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=AEBB96520616EFC115D3ADA6A48ABD3F)\\\\\n\\\\\nDubai Parks and Resorts\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 20% discount on entry tickets\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/dubai-parks-resorts-fab \"Dubai Parks and Resorts\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/view-at-the-palm/theview-palm-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=E1A0AEF853EFBE036BFF51870CE83F24)\\\\\n\\\\\nThe View at the Palm\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n20% Discount on entry tickets\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/view-at-the-palm \"The View at the Palm\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/wild-wadi-waterpark/wild-wadi-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=9597F4570A7E6738792343EB01A0026C)\\\\\n\\\\\nWild Wadi Waterpark\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nUnlock special discounts on entry passes and more\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/wild-wadi-waterpark-fab \"Wild Wadi Waterpark\")\n\n[![Al Futtaim](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/alfuttaim_img.jpg?h=200&iar=0&w=300&hash=AC9CBB629C73A7617AFBA345ABDAF7C7)\\\\\n\\\\\nAl Futtaim\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n0% Easy Payment Plan at Al Futtaim brands\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/alfuttaimepp \"Al Futtaim\")\n\n## Beyond Benefits: Your card has you covered.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg)![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg)\n\nBalance Transfers\n\nSettle your outstanding balances with other Bank Credit Cards within the UAE by transferring to your FAB Credit Card.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/balance-transfer)\n\nQuick Cash\n\nGet easy access to cash when you need it the most.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/quick-cash)\n\nEasy Payment Plans\n\nGet easy instalment plans with competitive rates and flexible repayments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/easy-payment-plan)\n\nStanding Instructions for Recurring Payments\n\nEnjoy the convenience of automatic bill payments with our Standing Instructions facility for up to 20 bill payments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-recurring-plans)\n\nStanding Instruction for a One Time Payment\n\nMake payments to over 75 partners including school fees, utility bills, insurance premiums, property maintenance fees and more.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-one-time-payments)\n\nCredit Card Bill Payments\n\nPay your credit card bills for FREE through any of our payment channels.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-card-bill-payment)\n\nCredit Shield\n\nCredit Shield helps you when it matters the most.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-shield)\n\nWallet Shield\n\nCovers against fraudulent transactions on your lost or stolen credit cards, stolen cash and theft of identification or keys.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/wallet-shield)\n\nAccident Care Plan\n\nGet coverage of up to  150,000 to cater to unforeseen eventualities.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/accident-care-plan)\n\nEnhanced Security for Online Purchases\n\nSafeguard the online transactions you make with your FAB credit card with a One-Time Password (OTP).\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/enhanced-security)\n\nUtility Bill Payments\n\nPay your bills through our convenient banking channels.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/utility-bill-payments)\n\nChip and PIN\n\nYour FAB credit card has an encrypted chip along with enhanced security using a Personal Identification Number (PIN).\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/chip-and-pin)\n\nPayment Partners\n\nTake a look at our extensive list of payment partners.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/payment-partners)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/forms/forms-en.jpg?h=900&iar=0&w=704&hash=A93D982D8E0977512DF592F8F85E8E96)\n\n## Request a Callback\n\n(Optional)\n\n(Optional)\n\n93/255\n\n(Optional)\n\n(Optional)\n\n0/255\n\n## Enter your details below\n\nWe will call you back within 24 hours to proceed with your inquiry. (\\*denotes mandatory fields)\n\nFirst Name \\*\n\nFirst Name \\*\n\n0/25\n\nLast Name \\*\n\nLast Name \\*\n\n0/25\n\nCompany name (Optional)\n\nCompany name (Optional)\n\nPhone Number \\*\n\nPhone Number \\*\n\n0/10\n\nEmail \\*\n\nEmail \\*\n\nEmirate \\*\n\nEmirate \\*\n\nNationality \\*\n\nNationality \\*\n\nSalary per month \\*\n\nSalary per month \\*\n\n##### Do you own a car?\n\nYes\n\nNo\n\n##### How much do you spend on utility bills per month?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\n##### How much do you spend on entertainment per month?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\n##### How many times do you travel per year?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\n##### How much do you spend on education per year?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\nI hereby authorise First Abu Dhabi Bank to obtain a credit information report on me from the AI Etihad Credit Bureau(or any successor organisation).\n\nI read and accept the **[Terms and Conditions](https://www.bankfab.com/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated)**.\n\nApply now\n\nreCAPTCHA\n\nRecaptcha requires verification.\n\nprotected by **reCAPTCHA**\n\n## Find out more about our Fees, Terms and Conditions.\n\n[Schedule of Fees\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fees-and-charges/credit-card.pdf?view=1 \"\")\n\n[FAB Rewards Terms and Conditions\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/fab-reward-programmes/fab-rewards-terms-and-conditions-en.pdf?view=1 \"\")\n\n[Terms and Conditions\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/fab-cashback-creditcard-tnc-en-01082024.pdf?view=1 \"\")\n\n**WARNING:** If you make only the minimum repayment/payment each period, you will pay more in interest/profit/fees and it will take you longer to pay off your outstanding balance.\n\n## Need more help? Get in touch.\n\nContact us anytime for further assistance or check out our [FAQ page](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/help-and-support/faqs) for more information.\n\n| For customers within the UAE | For customers outside of the UAE |\n| --- | --- |\n| ![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg) | [600 52 5500](tel:600525500) | ![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg) | [+971 2 681 1511](tel:009712681151) |\n\n![](https://page-source.com/resizeimage.ashx?ig=www.bankfab.com&sz=11444)",
