-ae/?card=E23CD4F2-47FF-46A7-9EED-E1400C5812E5&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_keyword=not%20provided&amp;utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fcashback-credit-card&amp;tst_id=null#apply-now\" class=\"button ev_1 button-text-simple-children button-contained-secondary no-popup\" datalayertext=\"Hero_GetYourCard\" aria-label=\"Get your cashback credit card\" title=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" data-text=\"\"><div>Apply now</div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"9ea240fb-12f4-4b6b-aea3-36327749180f\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_9ea240fb-12f4-4b6b-aea3-36327749180f\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"cardDigital add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"wrap content flex-it\"><div class=\"cardDigital__media flex-it flex-justify-center flex-align-item-center\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2026/cashback-credit-card-amazon-gift-card-offer/conventional-offer-tile-spring-madness.jpg?h=702&amp;iar=0&amp;w=818&amp;hash=C474618D757F3C282FDBE78B912A6AE8\"></figure></div><div class=\"cardDigital__text flex-it flex-justify-center flex-align-item-center flex-wrap\"><div class=\"auto\"><div class=\"css-1msmj7m\"><div class=\"global-rich-text richText richTextCss\"><p>Apply for a new FAB Cashback Credit Card by 15 May 2026 and you’ll get an Amazon Gift Card worth up to  1,000.</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>Apply for your new card by 15 May 2026.</li>\n    <li>Spend  10,000 to receive a  1,000 Amazon Gift Card or  5,000 to receive a  500 Amazon Gift Card within 30 days of when your card is issued.</li>\n    <li>Benefit from a first year fee waiver. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><small><a style=\"text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2026/cashback-credit-card-amazon-gift-card-offer/cashback-credit-card-amazon-gift-card-offer_en.pdf?view=1\" target=