elect categories and all other spending, please read the below Terms &amp; Conditions PDF.</li>\n    <li>Cashback will be processed in equivalent FAB Rewards, redeemable instantly on the FAB Mobile app.</li>\n</ul></div></div></section><section id=\"660a0352-c284-4c0d-84b1-a8f10fbc3dd8\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_660a0352-c284-4c0d-84b1-a8f10fbc3dd8\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content add-margins margin-bottom-0 margin-top-0\"><section id=\"b0b7dbce-7117-44c2-963b-e3da25cc5f69\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_b0b7dbce-7117-44c2-963b-e3da25cc5f69\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">Lifestyle</h2><div class=\"group-tabs\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"tabs-carousel-wrapper tabs-component-pc\"><div id=\"tabs-car-control-prev-15390\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-left tabs-carousel-control-hidden\"><div></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal tabs-carousel swiper-backface-hidden\" role=\"tablist\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); transition-duration: 300ms;\"><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\" id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\"><button id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab tabs-carousel-tab-active\">Benefits</button></div><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\" id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\"><button id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab\">Additional Information</button></div></div><div class=\"swiper-pagination swiper-paginatio