ass=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/2.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=E18468F856DDB3C60CE046DEC3B550B5\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Carrefour online discounts</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Additional_Information\" class=\"tab-item-container d-none d-none\"><div class=\"bullet-point-listing content remove-seperator\"><ul class=\"bpl-items hide-or-variation-one\"><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">40% off Talabat orders</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Enjoy great restaurant deals! Get 40% off orders on the Talabat app with up to &nbsp;40 off each order, four times a month with a minimum order of &nbsp;100. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about discounts Talabat orders\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/pdf/talabat-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Head to the cinema with tickets for  20</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Watch all the latest movies with two movie tickets a month for &nbsp;20 at Reel Cinemas, Cine Royal and Star Cinemas. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about cinema offers\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/lifestyle/cinema-en.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Carrefour online discounts</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p> 40 off Carrefour online when you spend a minimum of &nbsp;250 once every month. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about Carrefour online discounts\" href=\"https://www.carrefouruae.com/mafuae/en/n/c/clp_mastercard-world-worldelite\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free coffee with Costa</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Grab a free coffee with Costa! Get up to 2 Costa coffees at Dubai Airport plus another 2 items (from a selected list). <a aria-label=\"Learn more about Free coffee with Costa” rel=\" noopener=\"\" noreferrer\"=\"\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/194249/costa-coffee-complimentary-food-drink/0/4007/options/sortBy/popularity/category/1021/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a>*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Cashback on other spending and shopping</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>You don’t need to spend on groceries alone to save! Earn 1% extra cashback on all your other spending, save with every purchase. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about cashback on spending and shopping\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/fab-cashback-creditcard-tnc-en-01082024.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-4\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Enjoy 10% off incredible fashion with Farfetch</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>This one’s for the trendsetters and the fashion fans. Get 10% off Farfetch.com when you spend a minimum of USD 300. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about discount with Farfetch\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/shopping/product/163188/farfetch-discount/0/4007/options/cardType/3/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a>*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-5\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">15% off Bicester Village Shopping Collection</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>You can also enjoy 15% off when you shop with the Bicester Village Shopping Collection (Applicable on shopping packages, chauffer drive experiences and shopping express). <a aria-label=\"Learn more about Bicester Village Shopping Collection\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/shopping/product/163190/bicester-village-shopping-collection/0/4007/options/cardType/3/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a>*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-6 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><small>*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit <a href=\"https://www.priceless.com/benefits-mea\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">priceless.com</a> for the latest updates.</small></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"ff2f1b2f-9e89-417c-9f72-4c416aa4be5e\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_ff2f1b2f-9e89-417c-9f72-4c416aa4be5e\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">Travel</h2><div class=\"group-tabs\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"tabs-carousel-wrapper tabs-component-pc\"><div id=\"tabs-car-control-prev-31953\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-left tabs-carousel-control-hidden\"><div></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal tabs-carousel swiper-backface-hidden\" role=\"tablist\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); transition-duration: 300ms;\"><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\" id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\"><button id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab tabs-carousel-tab-active\">Benefits</button></div><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\" id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\"><button id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab\">Additional Information</button></div></div><div class=\"swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-clickable swiper-pagination-bullets swiper-pagination-horizontal\"><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-active\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet\"></span></div></div><div id=\"tabs-car-control-next-31953\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-right\"><div></div></div></div><div class=\"Dropdown-root tabs-dropdown tabs-component-mobile\"><div class=\"Dropdown-control tabs-dropdown-label-wrapper\" aria-haspopup=\"listbox\"><div class=\"Dropdown-placeholder tabs-dropdown-label is-selected\">Benefits</div><div class=\"Dropdown-arrow-wrapper\"><div class=\"tabs-dropdown-arrow \"></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Benefits\" class=\"tab-item-container showing d-none\"><div class=\"columns-splitter add-margins\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/4.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=80BA770C684B8E6C8060FC65354D79A1\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">40% off MakeMyTrip bookings</span></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/5.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=445AEDB431DAFFE0871D58B6A5A346B2\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Free airport lounge access and airport transfers</span></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/cashback-credit-card/v11/icons/6.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=7FF3DCC0804E0EC28DC9AE56DB01514C\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Cashback on travel spends</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Additional_Information\" class=\"tab-item-container d-none d-none\"><div class=\"bullet-point-listing content remove-seperator\"><ul class=\"bpl-items hide-or-variation-one\"><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">40% off MakeMyTrip bookings</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Save big with exclusive travel deals, get up to 40% off flights and hotel bookings through MakeMyTrip. You will also receive a 10% bonus in your MMT wallet (up to  100) for each traveller, with a maximum of five people per booking. Enjoy a 20% discount on hotel bookings, up to  300. You’ll also get a 20% bonus in your MMT wallet, up to  300, when you spend at least  300. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about MakeMyTrip bookings terms and conditions\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/travel/makemytrip-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free worldwide airport lounge access</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Enjoy free worldwide airport lounge access for you and your plus one! Relax with up to 8 free lounge visits per year, while your plus one receives 6 complimentary visits. Elevate your travel experience with these exclusive lounge benefits. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about airport lounge access\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/168080/world-mastercard-lounge-program-dp/0/4007/options/category/509/location/19588/cardType/3/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a>*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Save more with 3% cashback on spending when travelling</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Save more with 3% cashback on travel and enjoy a variety of exclusive travel offers.  <a aria-label=\"Learn more about cashback on travel terms and conditions\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/fab-cashback-creditcard-tnc-en-01082024.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free airport transfers</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Benefit from hassle-free transportation with 1 free airport transfer. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about Free airport transfers\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/195122/complimentary-airport-transfers-with-careem/0/4007/options/sortBy/popularity/category/1021/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a>*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><small>*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit <a href=\"https://www.priceless.com/benefits-mea\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">priceless.com</a> for the latest updates.</small></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section><section id=\"get-your-card\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_get-your-card\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"cards-list-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-cards-wrapper content\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card-sub\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card-content\"><div class=\"cllc-left\"><div class=\"cl-card-header\"><div class=\"cl-card-header-image-wrapper\"><img class=\"cl-card-header-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/overview/cards-images/fab-cashback-credit-card-2.png?iar=0&amp;hash=3B44ACA25D612D307F7763139276AD71\"></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-footer cllc-footer-pc without-padding\"></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-description cllc-right\"><h2 class=\"cl-card-desc-title\">Apply now for a FAB Cashback Credit Card</h2><div class=\"global-rich-text cl-card-desc-text\"><p>Ready to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.</p></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-features\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature\"><p class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-title\">Minimum Monthly Salary</p><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-value\"> <b>5,000</b></div></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-wrapper\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-icon\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/icon-percentage\" alt=\"Percentage Alt\" title=\"icon.percentage.title\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-text\">Ready to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.</div></div></div><div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;\"><a data-isonboarding=\"true\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-button-type=\"type_a\" id=\"4859efd3-2e31-4353-9866-8c06355d488b\" field=\"[object Object]\" href=\"https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=E23CD4F2-47FF-46A7-9EED-E1400C5812E5&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_keyword=not%20provided&amp;utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fcashback-credit-card&amp;tst_id=null#apply-now\" class=\"button ev_1 button-text-simple-children button-contained-primary\" datalayertext=\"Apply now\" aria-label=\"Apply now\" title=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" data-text=\"\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\" style=\"display: inline-block; max-width: 126px; width: 100%; text-align: center; margin: 0px;\"><div>Apply now</div></a></div></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-footer cllc-footer-mobile without-padding\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"fd08db3b-071a-4a86-9e2a-829fdfdaf8aa\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_fd08db3b-071a-4a86-9e2a-829fdfdaf8aa\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"cardDigital add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"wrap content flex-it\"><div class=\"cardDigital__media flex-it flex-justify-center flex-align-item-center\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2025/mclaren-f1-cards-offer/10-card-pdp-promo-tile-mclaren-f1.jpg?h=832&amp;iar=0&amp;w=1024&amp;hash=C9567B08FE8C6813EBAD068966F16FEA\"></figure></div><div class=\"cardDigital__text flex-it flex-justify-center flex-align-item-center flex-wrap\"><div class=\"auto\"><div class=\"css-1csuz7o\"><div class=\"global-rich-text richText richTextCss\"><p>As the Official Race Partner of the McLaren F1 Team, FAB is bringing the thrill of the track to your wallet.</p>\n<p>For a limited time, your card will transform with exclusive McLaren F1 artwork.</p>\n<p>Plus, subscribe to our McLaren Racing Mastercard Pass and enjoy exclusive fan content and freebies, and a chance to win a trip to the McLaren Technology Centre in the UK and much more.</p></div></div><div class=\"wrapButtons\"><a data-isonboarding=\"false\" data-button-type=\"type_a\" id=\"98b14dad-172b-4514-a14a-e879049e9668\" field=\"[object Object]\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/promotions/mclaren-f1-cards-offer\" class=\"button ev_1 button-arrow button-text-simple-children button-text-primary-arrow-right view button-outlined-primary\" datalayertext=\"Learn more\" aria-label=\"Learn more about McLaren Racing Mastercard Pass\" title=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" data-text=\"\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\"><div>Learn more</div><div class=\"button-arrow-wrapper\"><div class=\"button-arrow button-arrow-blue\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg\" alt=\"icon.button-arrow-blue.alt\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></div><div class=\"button-arrow button-arrow-white\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg\" alt=\"icon.button-arrow-blue.alt\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></div><div class=\"button-arrow button-arrow-red\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg\" alt=\"icon.button-arrow-blue.alt\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></div><div class=\"button-arrow button-arrow-black\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg\" alt=\"icon.button-arrow-blue.alt\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"how-to-video\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_how-to-video\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content add-margins margin-top-60\"><section id=\"0223f675-4df9-4efc-ae37-2039b63dc3a2\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_0223f675-4df9-4efc-ae37-2039b63dc3a2\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"columns-splitter add-margins\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-6 col-xl-6\"><div class=\"content content-component add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-20\"><div class=\"global-rich-text description\"><h2 class=\"header3\">How to easily apply for your credit card online</h2>\n<p>Watch this short video and see how you can apply for a FAB  credit card online in just a few minutes.</p>\n\n</div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-5 col-lg-6 col-xl-6\"><div class=\"video-component content add-margins margin-bottom-0 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"fullscreen\"><div style=\"width: 640px; height: 360px;\"><div data-vimeo-initialized=\"true\" style=\"width: 