swiper-pagination-bullet-active-main\" style=\"left: 0px;\"></span><span class=\"custom-pagination-cardlisting swiper-pagination-bullet swiper-pagination-bullet-active-main\" style=\"left: 0px;\"></span></div></div></div></section><section id=\"7115a1a0-faaf-428c-8b48-7828832242d0\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_7115a1a0-faaf-428c-8b48-7828832242d0\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"CarouselWithInformativeCards\"><div class=\"carousel-wrapper carousel-wrapper-light add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"content carousel-slides\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"carousel\"><div class=\"carousel-heading-wrapper\"><div class=\"carousel-heading\"><h2 class=\"carousel-heading-title carousel-heading-title-light\">Beyond Benefits: Your card has you covered.</h2></div><div class=\"carousel-controls\"><button id=\"carousel-control-prev-83598\" class=\"carousel-control control-rotated control-disabled\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Previous slide\" disabled=\"\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></button><button id=\"carousel-control-next-83598\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Next slide\" class=\"carousel-control\" tabindex=\"0\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></button></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal carousel\" role=\"\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transition-duration: 300ms; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);\"><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-1\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Balance Transfers</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Settle your outstanding balances with other Bank Credit Cards within the UAE by transferring to your FAB Credit Card.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/balance-transfer\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-2\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Quick Cash</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Get easy access to cash when you need it the most.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/quick-cash\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Easy Payment Plans</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Get easy instalment plans with competitive rates and flexible repayments.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/easy-payment-plan\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-4\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Standing Instructions for Recurring Payments</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Enjoy the convenience of automatic bill payments with our Standing Instructions facility for up to 20 bill payments. </p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-recurring-plans\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-5\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Standing Instruction for a One Time Payment </span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Make payments to over 75 partners including school fees, utility bills, insurance premiums, property maintenance fees and more.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-one-time-payments\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-6\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Credit Card Bill Payments</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Pay your credit card bills for FREE through any of our payment channels.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-card-bill-payment\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Credit Shield</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Credit Shield helps you when it matters the most.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-shield\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-5\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Wallet Shield</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Covers against fraudulent transactions on your lost or stolen credit cards, stolen cash and theft of identification or keys.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/wallet-shield\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Accident Care Plan</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Get coverage of up to &nbsp;150,000 to cater to  unforeseen eventualities.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important;\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/accident-care-plan\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-5\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Enhanced Security for Online Purchases</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Safeguard the online transactions you make with your FAB credit card with a One-Time Password (OTP).</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/enhanced-security\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-6\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Utility Bill Payments</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Pay your bills through our convenient banking channels.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/utility-bill-payments\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Chip and PIN</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Your FAB credit card has an encrypted chip along with enhanced security using a Personal Identification Number (PIN).</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/chip-and-pin\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-5\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Payment Partners</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Take a look at our extensive list of payment partners.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/payment-partners\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=