ake you longer to pay off your outstanding balance.</p>\n</div></div></section></div></section><section id=\"064fc922-8ba8-4312-922d-477ccc5751d7\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_064fc922-8ba8-4312-922d-477ccc5751d7\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content add-margins margin-bottom-80 margin-top-80\"><section id=\"fa44b891-2d55-4e36-95e9-a1693cf0e588\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_fa44b891-2d55-4e36-95e9-a1693cf0e588\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"columns-splitter add-margins\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-5 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"content content-component add-margins margin-bottom-0 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"global-rich-text description\"><h2 class=\"header3\">Need more help? Get in touch.</h2>\n<p>Contact us anytime for further assistance or check out our <a href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/help-and-support/faqs\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">FAQ page</a> for more information.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-7 col-xl-8\"><div class=\"table-component content add-margins margin-bottom-0 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"table-component-table-wrapper\"><table role=\"presentation\" class=\"talk-to-us-table\" style=\"min-width: 400px;\">\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th style=\"width:50%;\" colspan=\"2\">For customers within the UAE</th>\n            <th style=\"width:50%;\" colspan=\"2\">For customers outside of the UAE</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"adjustable-width\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></td>\n            <td><a href=\"tel:600525500\" datalayertext=\"Customer Service\" class=\"no-popup\" aria-label=\"600525500\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-s