          "markdown": "[Skip to content](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite#main-content-section)\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n- English\n\nEnglish\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  - [العربية\\\\\n    \\\\\n    العربية](https://www.bankfab.com/ar-ae/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n[![Branch locator](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/location.svg?iar=0&hash=BE0DB30E697196E30449E6F9E2217AA9)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/branch-locator \"\")[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/phone.svg?iar=0&hash=9081683D4B6CA5EF886D8EC61792E421)Customer Care](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/contact-us \"\")![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)Login\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)\n\n## Login\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\nPersonal Banking\n\n- [Personal Online Banking (UAE)](https://online.bankfab.com/PersonalBankingWeb/login)\n- [Ratibi Prepaid Card Balance Enquiry](https://ppc.magnati.com/ppc-inquiry)\n\nCorporate & Investment\n\n- [FAB Business Portal](https://business.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABeAccess - Corporate Online Banking](https://fabeaccess.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABOnline Banking Cash (Corporate)](https://online.bankfab.com/fabonline)\n- [FABOnline Banking Trade (Corporate)](https://fabeaccesstrade.bankfab.com/fabonlinetrade/portal)\n- [iBanking Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking.bankfab.com/iportalweb/)\n- [IPO/RI Subscription](https://www.bankfab.com/v1/en-ae/investment-banking/iposubscription)\n- [FAB Securities Services (INSIGHT)](https://fss.bankfab.com/)\n- [iBanking ADGM Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking-adgm.bankfab.com/iportalweb)\n\nFAB Securities\n\n- [FABS Online](https://www.securitiesfab.com/EInvest)\n- [FABS Research Portal](https://fabsresearch.bankfab.com/Researchportal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)Login\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)\n\n## Login\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\nPersonal Banking\n\n- [Personal Online Banking (UAE)](https://online.bankfab.com/PersonalBankingWeb/login)\n- [Ratibi Prepaid Card Balance Enquiry](https://ppc.magnati.com/ppc-inquiry)\n\nCorporate & Investment\n\n- [FAB Business Portal](https://business.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABeAccess - Corporate Online Banking](https://fabeaccess.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABOnline Banking Cash (Corporate)](https://online.bankfab.com/fabonline)\n- [FABOnline Banking Trade (Corporate)](https://fabeaccesstrade.bankfab.com/fabonlinetrade/portal)\n- [iBanking Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking.bankfab.com/iportalweb/)\n- [IPO/RI Subscription](https://www.bankfab.com/v1/en-ae/investment-banking/iposubscription)\n- [FAB Securities Services (INSIGHT)](https://fss.bankfab.com/)\n- [iBanking ADGM Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking-adgm.bankfab.com/iportalweb)\n\nFAB Securities\n\n- [FABS Online](https://www.securitiesfab.com/EInvest)\n- [FABS Research Portal](https://fabsresearch.bankfab.com/Researchportal)\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_burger-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\n[Personal](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n[Business](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/business-banking)\n\n[Corporate](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/corporate-banking)\n\n[Investment Banking](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/investment-banking)\n\n[Islamic](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/islamic-banking)\n\n[Private](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/private)\n\n[About FAB](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/about-fab)\n\n[Subsidiaries](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/subsidiaries)\n\n[Insights](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/insights)\n\nInternational\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal \"First Abu Dhabi Bank home page\")\n\n![Search](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/banner/cc-banner-lowrate-en-09.jpg?h=609&iar=0&w=1440&hash=99C2F5F9628D819FD2C6524256E1CA2F)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/etihad-guest-infinite-credit-card-466x327.png?h=327&iar=0&w=466&hash=A94C5349C43D9A838240544FC43BFB0B)\n\n# Etihad Guest Infinite Credit Card\n\nGo beyond. Travel better with exclusive Etihad offers, more miles and special discounts.\n\n[Apply Now](https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=11AAE4D4-512E-47A3-B0D3-1C586982FE42&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=none&utm_keyword=not%20provided&utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fetihad-guest-infinite&tst_id=null#apply-now \"\")\n\n## Elevate every travel experience with exciting benefits.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/2-etihad-guest-miles-bonus.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=EF71512CF4737ABD660FD7524B733EA3)\n\n### A 55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus\n\nEnjoy more miles with a 55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/3-etihad-miles-on-spending.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=77C221516AFB5C1E82F55CFFE3EE1B81)\n\n### Up to 7.5 Etihad Guest Miles on spending\n\nYou can earn up to 7.5 Etihad Guest Miles for every  10 you spend.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/4-airport-lounge-access.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=879C84E4C77142987FC8EBF9B58B25AC)\n\n### Airport lounge access\n\nComfort comes first with free worldwide airport lounge access.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/5-fast-track-etihad-gold-membership.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=FAADBEBED1A83997178973405A10CBE5)\n\n### Fast track your Etihad Guest Gold membership\n\nYou’ll be able to move up and fast track your Etihad Guest Gold membership.\n\n## Elevate every travel experience with exciting benefits.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/2-etihad-guest-miles-bonus.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=EF71512CF4737ABD660FD7524B733EA3)\n\n### A 55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus\n\nEnjoy more miles with a 55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/3-etihad-miles-on-spending.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=77C221516AFB5C1E82F55CFFE3EE1B81)\n\n### Up to 7.5 Etihad Guest Miles on spending\n\nYou can earn up to 7.5 Etihad Guest Miles for every  10 you spend.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/4-airport-lounge-access.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=879C84E4C77142987FC8EBF9B58B25AC)\n\n### Airport lounge access\n\nComfort comes first with free worldwide airport lounge access.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/highlights/5-fast-track-etihad-gold-membership.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=FAADBEBED1A83997178973405A10CBE5)\n\n### Fast track your Etihad Guest Gold membership\n\nYou’ll be able to move up and fast track your Etihad Guest Gold membership.\n\n##  30,000\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n##  2,500\n\nAnnual Fees\n\n##  30,000\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n##  2,500\n\nAnnual Fees\n\n## Etihad\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/etihad-1.svg?iar=0&hash=4854D7134EC5FCCDAA72576958738523)\n\n55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/etihad-2.svg?iar=0&hash=D8B449E9B38AC9D5243514800DB30812)\n\n75% Miles Discount Voucher\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/etihad-3.svg?iar=0&hash=967863AF84D7078F6FAA14F19DD06F42)\n\nGet fast tracked to Etihad Guest Gold status\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nA 55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus\n\n\n\n\n\nGet an Etihad Guest Miles welcome bonus of 55,000 miles on card activation. Supplementary cards receive a bonus too, with 5,000 miles.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n75% Miles Discount Voucher\n\n\n\n\n\nSpend  200,000 a year on your card and get a 75% Etihad Guest Miles discount voucher. This gives you 75% off the miles needed for a reward flight to any destination and in any class of your choice.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGet fast tracked to Etihad Guest Gold status\n\n\n\n\n\nGet on the fast track to become an Etihad Guest Gold member faster than usual by just completing one return flight with Etihad within six months of card activation.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree inflight Wi-Fi voucher\n\n\n\n\n\nCruise the skies with 4 free in-flight Wi-Fi vouchers for up to 24 hours of uptime on Etihad flights when you first get an Etihad Guest Infinite credit card.\n\n\nThe vouchers are valid for a period of one year from the date of issuance and will be sent by Etihad Airways to your registered email address.\n\n\n\n\nFor further details kindly refer to: [Etihad Guest Credit Cards FAQs](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/etihad-guest-credit-cards-faqs.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n\n## Earn Miles\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/earn-miles-1.svg?iar=0&hash=16D1547CC9D25120C7C0B35B5093FD06)\n\nEarn more Etihad Guest Miles on spending\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/earn-miles-2.svg?iar=0&hash=51BA5E3717545BC772D8637481111A9E)\n\nEarn more Tier Miles\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/earn-miles-3.svg?iar=0&hash=2C1DE4025306891B1081DC9920CBE07E)\n\nOptional Miles Accelerator Programme\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nEarn more Etihad Guest Miles on spending\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy earning several miles on your spending. You’ll get 3.5 miles for every  10 spent on domestic transactions, 6 miles for non-AED international transactions and 7 miles for every  10 spent with Etihad or Etihad Airways partners.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nEarn more Tier Miles\n\n\n\n\n\nEarn More Etihad Tier Miles with 2.5 Tier Miles for every  10 you spend both in the UAE and abroad.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nOptional Miles Accelerator Programme\n\n\n\n\n\nEarn 7.5 Etihad Guest Miles for every  10 spent on all purchases with an optional enrolment into the Miles Accelerator Programme, for just  250 per month.\n\n\nOR\n\n## Travel\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/travel-1.svg?iar=0&hash=8B401760CD01E92E05D2FA8C51EF4067)\n\nDiscounted airport transfers\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/travel-2.svg?iar=0&hash=3AB26B6B0CBB9715F73E2B8C41FD2E30)\n\nAirport Meet and Greet Services\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/travel-3.svg?iar=0&hash=AD38230431FD7CE026C3009FAB0C3693)\n\nFree airport lounge access\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nDiscounted airport transfers\n\n\n\n\n\nGet to the airport with ease. Enjoy 6 discounted airport transfers a year from  40 (within city service) or  100 (inter-city service). Eligible cardholders can book the service through [booking.enatravels.com](https://booking.enatravels.com/) at least 2 working days prior to their travel/ required drop-off or pick-up date or call on [04-8524856](tel:04-8524856) or email on [fabtransfers@enatravels.com](mailto:fabtransfers@enatravels.com).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nAirport Meet and Greet Services\n\n\n\n\n\nGet a personalised greeting and enjoy an exceptional airport experience at over 450 global destinations via YQ Now Group at a 25% discount of retail rates. Cardholders can book via [https://cemea.yqnowgroup.com/](https://cemea.yqnowgroup.com/) and applicable discount is applied directly to the transaction\\*.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree airport lounge access\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy unlimited complimentary access for the cardholder and an accompanying guest at over 1,000 airport lounges across the globe\\*.\n\n\nOR\n\nServices offered and supported by VISA. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [www.visamiddleeast.com](https://ae.visamiddleeast.com/en_AE/pay-with-visa/find-a-card/infinite.html) for the latest updates.\n\n## Lifestyle\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/lifestyle-1.svg?iar=0&hash=741F86239214EBC22EFFF4D0CD575BCB)\n\nDiscounted cinema tickets\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/lifestyle-2.svg?iar=0&hash=61A8A527BAC8EDDA9DF97EDE513AF829)\n\nGolf discounts\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/lifestyle-3.svg?iar=0&hash=080CEEA261850C4CB581C55F7519A61E)\n\n24/7 Travel Concierge Service\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nDiscounted cinema tickets\n\n\n\n\n\nGet six discounted cinema tickets a month for  20 at Reel Cinemas, Cine Royal and Star Cinemas.\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGolf discounts\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy exclusive discounts at highly prestigious golf courses.\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n24/7 Travel Concierge Service\n\n\n\n\n\nMake your trip even better with a 24-hour Travel Concierge Service available to help you with your travel-related tasks. Please call [800 0441 3487](tel:80004413487) or [+971 4 361 1234](tel:+97143611234) to take advantage of this service.\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nSpecial Visa offers\n\n\n\n\n\nHundreds more top-class offers are available to Etihad Guest Infinite Credit Cardholders.\\*\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Services offered and supported by VISA. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [www.visamiddleeast.com](https://ae.visamiddleeast.com/en_AE/pay-with-visa/find-a-card/infinite.html) for the latest updates.\n\n## Protection\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/protection-1.svg?iar=0&hash=A5A91BF4055F56AE7C23D0A65B434F4B)\n\nInternational Medical and Travel Assistance\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/protection-2.svg?iar=0&hash=1E4765C04B489E2E7EAE5E5A67544475)\n\nTravel Accident Insurance\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/protection-3.svg?iar=0&hash=9FB0931C923BF7B57C444056824D74E4)\n\nBuyers Protection and Extended Warranty\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nInternational Medical and Travel Assistance\n\n\n\n\n\nStay covered for the unexpected during your travels with International Medical and Travel Assistance if you book with your Etihad Guest Infinite card. Receive extended benefits including emergency medical expenses, trip cancellation and delayed departure cover.\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nTravel Accident Insurance\n\n\n\n\n\nTravel with peace of mind. Receive complimentary Travel Accident Insurance of up to USD 2.5 million.\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nBuyers Protection and Extended Warranty\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy Buyers Protection and an Extended Warranty of 12 months beyond the manufacturer or retail warranty.\\*\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFraudulent Transaction Protection\n\n\n\n\n\nProtect yourself against fraud. Benefit from automatic protection against unauthorised transactions.\\*\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Services offered and supported by VISA. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [www.visamiddleeast.com](https://ae.visamiddleeast.com/en_AE/pay-with-visa/find-a-card/infinite.html) for the latest updates.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/overview/cards-images/etihad-guest-infinite-credit-card.png?iar=0&hash=49FB05A8AD47A1E85C647F30DC0590C9)\n\n## Apply now for an Etihad Guest Infinite Credit Card\n\nReady to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n **30,000**\n\n![Percentage Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/icon-percentage)\n\nReady to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.\n\n[Apply now](https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=11AAE4D4-512E-47A3-B0D3-1C586982FE42&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=none&utm_keyword=not%20provided&utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fetihad-guest-infinite&tst_id=null#apply-now \"\")\n\n## How to easily apply for your credit card online\n\nWatch this short video and see how you can apply for a FAB credit card online in just a few minutes.\n\nHow to Apply Online for a FAB Credit Card\\_EN from First Abu Dhabi Bank on Vimeo\n\n![video thumbnail](https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/2007623580-1ac9340085989191c4046e707c893dba9ffecac73264f60c91c1147d38d981a0-d?mw=80&q=85)\n\nPlaying in picture-in-picture\n\nPlay\n\n00:00\n\n01:33\n\nSettings\n\nQualityAuto\n\nPicture-in-PictureFullscreen\n\n;\n\n## Make the most of your credit card with FAB's fantastic offers\n\n[See all offers\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers \"\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/the-green-planet/green-planet-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=F3E4C17F9CC3E76374BDD41CB9FEDB5D)\\\\\n\\\\\nThe Green Planet\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 20% discount on day-passes\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/the-green-planet-fab \"The Green Planet\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/dubai-parks-resorts/dpr-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=AEBB96520616EFC115D3ADA6A48ABD3F)\\\\\n\\\\\nDubai Parks and Resorts\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 20% discount on entry tickets\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/dubai-parks-resorts-fab \"Dubai Parks and Resorts\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/view-at-the-palm/theview-palm-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=E1A0AEF853EFBE036BFF51870CE83F24)\\\\\n\\\\\nThe View at the Palm\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n20% Discount on entry tickets\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/view-at-the-palm \"The View at the Palm\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/wild-wadi-waterpark/wild-wadi-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=9597F4570A7E6738792343EB01A0026C)\\\\\n\\\\\nWild Wadi Waterpark\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nUnlock special discounts on entry passes and more\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/wild-wadi-waterpark-fab \"Wild Wadi Waterpark\")\n\n[![Al Futtaim](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/alfuttaim_img.jpg?h=200&iar=0&w=300&hash=AC9CBB629C73A7617AFBA345ABDAF7C7)\\\\\n\\\\\nAl Futtaim\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n0% Easy Payment Plan at Al Futtaim brands\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/alfuttaimepp \"Al Futtaim\")\n\n## Beyond Benefits: Your card has you covered.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg)![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg)\n\nBalance Transfers\n\nSettle your outstanding balances with other Bank Credit Cards within the UAE by transferring to your FAB Credit Card.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/balance-transfer)\n\nQuick Cash\n\nGet easy access to cash when you need it the most.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/quick-cash)\n\nEasy Payment Plans\n\nGet easy instalment plans with competitive rates and flexible repayments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/easy-payment-plan)\n\nStanding Instructions for Recurring Payments\n\nEnjoy the convenience of automatic bill payments with our Standing Instructions facility for up to 20 bill payments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-recurring-plans)\n\nStanding Instruction for a One Time Payment\n\nMake payments to over 75 partners including school fees, utility bills, insurance premiums, property maintenance fees and more.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-one-time-payments)\n\nCredit Card Bill Payments\n\nPay your credit card bills for FREE through any of our payment channels.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-card-bill-payment)\n\nCredit Shield\n\nCredit Shield helps you when it matters the most.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-shield)\n\nWallet Shield\n\nCovers against fraudulent transactions on your lost or stolen credit cards, stolen cash and theft of identification or keys.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/wallet-shield)\n\nAccident Care Plan\n\nGet coverage of up to  150,000 to cater to unforeseen eventualities.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/accident-care-plan)\n\nEnhanced Security for Online Purchases\n\nSafeguard the online transactions you make with your FAB credit card with a One-Time Password (OTP).\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/enhanced-security)\n\nUtility Bill Payments\n\nPay your bills through our convenient banking channels.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/utility-bill-payments)\n\nChip and PIN\n\nYour FAB credit card has an encrypted chip along with enhanced security using a Personal Identification Number (PIN).\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/chip-and-pin)\n\nPayment Partners\n\nTake a look at our extensive list of payment partners.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/payment-partners)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/forms/forms-en.jpg?h=900&iar=0&w=704&hash=A93D982D8E0977512DF592F8F85E8E96)\n\n## Request a Callback\n\n(Optional)\n\n(Optional)\n\n93/255\n\n(Optional)\n\n(Optional)\n\n0/255\n\n## Enter your details below\n\nWe will call you back within 24 hours to proceed with your inquiry. (\\*denotes mandatory fields)\n\nFirst Name \\*\n\nFirst Name \\*\n\n0/25\n\nLast Name \\*\n\nLast Name \\*\n\n0/25\n\nCompany name (Optional)\n\nCompany name (Optional)\n\nPhone Number \\*\n\nPhone Number \\*\n\n0/10\n\nEmail \\*\n\nEmail \\*\n\nEmirate \\*\n\nEmirate \\*\n\nNationality \\*\n\nNationality \\*\n\nSalary per month \\*\n\nSalary per month \\*\n\n##### Do you own a car?\n\nYes\n\nNo\n\n##### How much do you spend on utility bills per month?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\n##### How much do you spend on entertainment per month?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\n##### How many times do you travel per year?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\n##### How much do you spend on education per year?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\nI hereby authorise First Abu Dhabi Bank to obtain a credit information report on me from the AI Etihad Credit Bureau(or any successor organisation).\n\nI read and accept the **[Terms and Conditions](https://www.bankfab.com/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated)**.\n\nApply now\n\nreCAPTCHA\n\nRecaptcha requires verification.\n\nprotected by **reCAPTCHA**\n\n## Find out more about our Fees, Terms and Conditions.\n\n[Schedule of Fees and Charges\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fees-and-charges/credit-card.pdf?view=1 \"\")\n\n[Etihad Guest Credit Cards FAQs\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/etihad-guest-credit-cards-faqs.pdf?view=1 \"\")\n\n[Credit Card Terms and Conditions\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated \"\")\n\n**WARNING:** If you make only the minimum repayment/payment each period, you will pay more in interest/profit/fees and it will take you longer to pay off your outstanding balance.\n\n## Need more help? Get in touch.\n\nContact us anytime for further assistance or check out our [FAQ page](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/help-and-support/faqs) for more information.\n\n| For customers within the UAE | For customers outside of the UAE |\n| --- | --- |\n| ![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg) | [600 52 5500](tel:600525500) | ![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg) | [+971 2 681 1511](tel:009712681151) |\n\n![](https://page-source.com/resizeimage.ashx?ig=www.bankfab.com&sz=11444)",
