ia-labelledby=\"tab_Additional_Information\" class=\"tab-item-container d-none d-none\"><div class=\"bullet-point-listing content remove-seperator\"><ul class=\"bpl-items hide-or-variation-one\"><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">A 55,000 Etihad Guest Miles bonus</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get an Etihad Guest Miles welcome bonus of 55,000 miles on card activation. Supplementary cards receive a bonus too, with 5,000 miles.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">75% Miles Discount Voucher</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Spend  200,000 a year on your card and get a 75% Etihad Guest Miles discount voucher. This gives you 75% off the miles needed for a reward flight to any destination and in any class of your choice.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Get fast tracked to Etihad Guest Gold status</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get on the fast track to become an Etihad Guest Gold member faster than usual by just completing one return flight with Etihad within six months of card activation.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free inflight Wi-Fi voucher</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Cruise the skies with 4 free in-flight Wi-Fi vouchers for up to 24 hours of uptime on Etihad flights when you first get an Etihad Guest Infinite credit card.<br>\nThe vouchers are valid for a period of one year from the date of issuance and will be sent by Etihad Airways to your registered email address.<br>\n<br>\nFor further details kindly refer to: <a href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/card-specific/etihad-guest-credit-cards-faqs.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Etihad Guest Credit Cards FAQs</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"c356bdab-1f81-4d09-a1fc-c6e7165be275\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_c356bdab-1f81-4d09-a1fc-c6e7165be275\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">Earn Miles</h2><div class=\"group-tabs