.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/etihad-guest-infinite/icons/travel-3.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=AD38230431FD7CE026C3009FAB0C3693\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Free airport lounge access</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Additional_Information\" class=\"tab-item-container d-none d-none\"><div class=\"bullet-point-listing content remove-seperator\"><ul class=\"bpl-items hide-or-variation-one\"><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Discounted airport transfers</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get to the airport with ease. Enjoy 6 discounted airport transfers a year from  40 (within city service) or  100 (inter-city service). Eligible cardholders can book the service through <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://booking.enatravels.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">booking.enatravels.com</a> at least 2 working days prior to their travel/ required drop-off or pick-up date or call on <a href=\"tel:04-8524856\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">04-8524856</a> or email on <a href=\"mailto:fabtransfers@enatravels.com\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">fabtransfers@enatravels.com</a>.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Airport Meet and Greet Services</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get a personalised greeting and enjoy an exceptional airport experience at over 450 global destinations via YQ Now Group at a 25% discount of retail rates. Cardholders can book via <a href=\"https://cemea.yqnowgroup.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">https://cemea.yqnowgroup.com/</a> and applicable discount is applied directly to the transaction*.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free airport lounge access</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Enjoy unlimited complimentary access for the cardholder and an accompanying guest at over 1,000 airport lounges across the globe*.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><p><small>Services offered and supported by VISA. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit <a href=\"https://ae.visamiddleeast.com/en_AE/pay-with-visa/find-a-card/infinite.html\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">www.visamiddleeast.com</a> for the latest updates.</small></p>\n</div></div></di