Enjoy Buyers Protection and an Extended Warranty of 12 months beyond the manufacturer or retail warranty.*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Fraudulent Transaction Protection</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Protect yourself against fraud. Benefit from automatic protection against unauthorised transactions.*</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><p><small>*Services offered and supported by VISA. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit <a href=\"https://ae.visamiddleeast.com/en_AE/pay-with-visa/find-a-card/infinite.html\" target=\"_balnk\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">www.visamiddleeast.com</a> for the latest updates.</small></p></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section><section id=\"get-your-card\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_get-your-card\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"cards-list-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-cards-wrapper content\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card-sub\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card-content\"><div class=\"cllc-left\"><div class=\"cl-card-header\"><div class=\"cl-card-header-image-wrapper\"><img class=\"cl-card-header-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/overview/cards-images/etihad-guest-infinite-credit-card.png?iar=0&amp;hash=49FB05A8AD47A1E85C647F30DC0590C9\"></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-footer cllc-footer-pc without-padding\"></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-description cllc-right\"><h2 class=\"cl-card-desc-title\">Apply now for an Etihad Guest Infinite Credit Card</h2><div class=\"global-rich-text cl-card-desc-text\"><p>Ready to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.</p></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-features\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature\"><p class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-title\">Minimum Monthly Salary</p><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-value\"> <b>30,000</b></div></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-wrapper\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-icon\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/icon-percentage\" alt=\"Percentage Alt\" title=\"icon.percentage.title\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-text\">Ready to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.</div></div></div><div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;\"><a data-isonboarding=\"true\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-button-type=\"type_a\" id=\"3119123d-f16d-4ef5-bc7f-feae50d7c370\" field=\"[object Object]\" href=\"https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=11AAE4D4-512E-47A3-B0D3-1C586982FE42&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_keyword=not%20provided&amp;utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Fetihad-guest-infinite&amp;tst_id=null#apply-now\" class=\"button ev_1 button-text-simple-children button-contained-primary\" datalayertext=\"Apply now\" aria-label=\"Apply now for an Etihad Guest Infinite Credit Card\" title=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" data-text=\"\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\"