          "markdown": "[Skip to content](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card#main-content-section)\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n- English\n\nEnglish\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  - [العربية\\\\\n    \\\\\n    العربية](https://www.bankfab.com/ar-ae/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n[![Branch locator](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/location.svg?iar=0&hash=BE0DB30E697196E30449E6F9E2217AA9)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/branch-locator \"\")[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/phone.svg?iar=0&hash=9081683D4B6CA5EF886D8EC61792E421)Customer Care](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/contact-us \"\")![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)Login\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)\n\n## Login\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\nPersonal Banking\n\n- [Personal Online Banking (UAE)](https://online.bankfab.com/PersonalBankingWeb/login)\n- [Ratibi Prepaid Card Balance Enquiry](https://ppc.magnati.com/ppc-inquiry)\n\nCorporate & Investment\n\n- [FAB Business Portal](https://business.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABeAccess - Corporate Online Banking](https://fabeaccess.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABOnline Banking Cash (Corporate)](https://online.bankfab.com/fabonline)\n- [FABOnline Banking Trade (Corporate)](https://fabeaccesstrade.bankfab.com/fabonlinetrade/portal)\n- [iBanking Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking.bankfab.com/iportalweb/)\n- [IPO/RI Subscription](https://www.bankfab.com/v1/en-ae/investment-banking/iposubscription)\n- [FAB Securities Services (INSIGHT)](https://fss.bankfab.com/)\n- [iBanking ADGM Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking-adgm.bankfab.com/iportalweb)\n\nFAB Securities\n\n- [FABS Online](https://www.securitiesfab.com/EInvest)\n- [FABS Research Portal](https://fabsresearch.bankfab.com/Researchportal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)Login\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)\n\n## Login\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\nPersonal Banking\n\n- [Personal Online Banking (UAE)](https://online.bankfab.com/PersonalBankingWeb/login)\n- [Ratibi Prepaid Card Balance Enquiry](https://ppc.magnati.com/ppc-inquiry)\n\nCorporate & Investment\n\n- [FAB Business Portal](https://business.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABeAccess - Corporate Online Banking](https://fabeaccess.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABOnline Banking Cash (Corporate)](https://online.bankfab.com/fabonline)\n- [FABOnline Banking Trade (Corporate)](https://fabeaccesstrade.bankfab.com/fabonlinetrade/portal)\n- [iBanking Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking.bankfab.com/iportalweb/)\n- [IPO/RI Subscription](https://www.bankfab.com/v1/en-ae/investment-banking/iposubscription)\n- [FAB Securities Services (INSIGHT)](https://fss.bankfab.com/)\n- [iBanking ADGM Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking-adgm.bankfab.com/iportalweb)\n\nFAB Securities\n\n- [FABS Online](https://www.securitiesfab.com/EInvest)\n- [FABS Research Portal](https://fabsresearch.bankfab.com/Researchportal)\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_burger-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\n[Personal](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n[Business](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/business-banking)\n\n[Corporate](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/corporate-banking)\n\n[Investment Banking](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/investment-banking)\n\n[Islamic](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/islamic-banking)\n\n[Private](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/private)\n\n[About FAB](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/about-fab)\n\n[Subsidiaries](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/subsidiaries)\n\n[Insights](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/insights)\n\nInternational\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal \"First Abu Dhabi Bank home page\")\n\n![Search](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/fab-elite-header-banner.jpg?h=795&iar=0&w=2160&hash=F00C226DA834D598CC8AFC740F7C4207)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/fab-elite-cc-header.png?h=654&iar=0&w=932&hash=6ED79769C99255A2ED5E84A21DA53567)\n\n# FAB Elite Credit Card\n\nUnlock an elite lifestyle featuring exclusive access, extensive benefits and premium experiences.\n\n[Apply Now](https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=CC38F05A-D90F-454F-9192-E2769B4FFE35&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=none&utm_keyword=not%20provided&utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Ffab-elite-credit-card&tst_id=null#apply-now \"\")\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2026/rixos-staycation-credit-card-offer/may-staycation-tile.jpg?h=702&iar=0&w=768&hash=5A58C9ADCACD07ED0DA1EF2C0E625C8C)\n\nFor a limited time only, enjoy a free 1-night staycation at Rixos Bab Al Bahr in Ras Al Khaimah, including:\n\n- Half-board (breakfast and dinner) at the resort\n- A memorable experience for 2 adults and 2 children under 12\n- An elegant, Deluxe Room for added comfort\n\n[Conditions apply.](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2026/rixos-staycation-credit-card-offer/staycation_acquistion_campaign_tcs_travelelite_eng.pdf?view=1)\n\n[Find out more \\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/promotions/rixos-staycation-credit-card-offer \"\")\n\n## Elevate your lifestyle and enjoy exclusive advantages.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/1-exclusive-access.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=07FC3C939917236289B0DB7B2FEF030B)\n\n### Exclusive access to luxury beach clubs, gyms and more\n\nEnjoy exclusive access to luxury beach clubs, gyms, premium dining experiences and more.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/2-global-concierge.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=8267C336B76E5A8B4E6B149C57120BF2)\n\n### 24/7 global concierge and free valet parking\n\nAdded convenience with 24/7 global concierge and free valet parking.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/3-tree-planting.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=293F3FF30240F4739FF940A933BB7195)\n\n### Guaranteed gold gift and tree planting\n\nYou’ll get a guaranteed gold gift and tree planting with each card.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/4-fab-rewards.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=B3EB2F27A46FBF65F405CD1EF5F0B53A)\n\n### Up to 500,000 FAB Rewards on all your spending\n\nYou can earn up to 500,000 FAB Rewards on all your spending.\n\n## Elevate your lifestyle and enjoy exclusive advantages.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/1-exclusive-access.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=07FC3C939917236289B0DB7B2FEF030B)\n\n### Exclusive access to luxury beach clubs, gyms and more\n\nEnjoy exclusive access to luxury beach clubs, gyms, premium dining experiences and more.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/2-global-concierge.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=8267C336B76E5A8B4E6B149C57120BF2)\n\n### 24/7 global concierge and free valet parking\n\nAdded convenience with 24/7 global concierge and free valet parking.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/3-tree-planting.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=293F3FF30240F4739FF940A933BB7195)\n\n### Guaranteed gold gift and tree planting\n\nYou’ll get a guaranteed gold gift and tree planting with each card.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/benefits-images/4-fab-rewards.jpg?h=623&iar=0&w=552&hash=B3EB2F27A46FBF65F405CD1EF5F0B53A)\n\n### Up to 500,000 FAB Rewards on all your spending\n\nYou can earn up to 500,000 FAB Rewards on all your spending.\n\n##  40,000\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n##  1,200\n\nAnnual Fee\n\n##  40,000\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n##  1,200\n\nAnnual Fee\n\n## Experiences\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/experience-icon-01.svg?iar=0&hash=02E7CD320985951A9D4029CB24F9B921)\n\nFree access to 60+ beach clubs, gyms and sports clubs with ADV+\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/experience-icon-02.svg?iar=0&hash=05D44210A834F58B7FDD660AD1E46E1D)\n\nUp to 40% off at top restaurants in the UAE with ADV+\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/experience-icon-03.svg?iar=0&hash=FF9E1495354EE879A7F12019C03AA1FB)\n\nGet dedicated lifestyle concierge support 24/7\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree access to 60+ beach clubs, gyms and sports clubs with ADV+\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy free access to luxury beach clubs, gyms and sports centres across the UAE \\* Access is through the ADV+ app using a unique voucher code. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nUp to 40% off at top restaurants in the UAE with ADV+\n\n\n\n\n\nReceive a discount of up to 40% for you and your friends at some of the top hotel restaurants across the UAE. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGet dedicated lifestyle concierge support 24/7\n\n\n\n\n\nIf you would like assistance with travel planning, booking fine dining or access to exclusive events – call the 24/7 lifestyle concierge service to help you plan and book. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163202/world-elite-mastercard-concierge/0/4007/options/cardType/2/)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGuaranteed gift of gold from the FAB Rewards Shop\n\n\n\n\n\nSpend  500,000 a year or more on your card and you'll be rewarded with gold! To redeem just visit the FAB Rewards section on the FAB Mobile app and redeem your gold gift. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nEco-friendly benefits and Rewards\n\n\n\n\n\nFor each new card, we’ll plant a tree on your behalf with Give a Ghaf. Plus, earn 10 FAB Rewards at eco-friendly merchants including Kibsons, Emirates Bio Farm, Just Vegan, The Giving Movement, BON organic perfumes and over 200 more brands in the UAE. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Subject to an  10,000 monthly spend on the card. Beach / sport access is chargeable at  300 for each month the spend target is not met.\n\n## Lifestyle\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/lifestyle-icons-01.svg?iar=0&hash=5CF488DDEF2FDA783BC3E5A59E0F5140)\n\nEnjoy one-hour free valet parking at premium locations\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/lifestyle-icons-02.svg?iar=0&hash=2B169BC8E7C544C29AC9608999567A05)\n\nBuy one get one free movie ticket offer at Roxy Cinemas\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/lifestyle-icons-03.svg?iar=0&hash=C51F057BA4DF8F50206026EF4A8B48ED)\n\n20% off Emaar attractions\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nEnjoy one-hour free valet parking at premium locations\n\n\n\n\n\nGet a free hour of valet parking up to 5 times a month at premium UAE locations including Mall of the Emirates, City Walk, Dubai Mall, Yas Mall, Al Qana, Dubai Hills Mall and many more.\\* [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nBuy one get one free movie ticket offer at Roxy Cinemas\n\n\n\n\n\nPlus, enjoy eight movie tickets from  20 each per month at Reel, Royal, Star, VOX Cinemas.\\* [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n20% off Emaar attractions\n\n\n\n\n\nYou can avail an unlimited discount of up to 20% at KidZania, Dubai Aquarium & Underwater Zoo – Penguin Cove and Nursery Experience, The Storm Coaster and Zabeel Sports District. Learn more\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n20% off Dubai Holding attractions\n\n\n\n\n\nAn up to 20% unlimited discount at Wild Wadi, Dubai Parks and Resorts, Inside Burj Al Arab, The Green Planet and The View Palm.\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n30% off golf worldwide with Mastercard Golf Programme\n\n\n\n\n\nWith Mastercard’s’ Golf Programme by Thriwe - you can get 30% off, or one free guest on your next game of golf at selected golf clubs worldwide. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/sports/product/194217/mastercard-golf-program-by-thriwe/0/4007/options/category/507/location/19588/)\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Subject to an  10,000 monthly spend on the card. Cinema benefits / valet parking is chargeable at  100 (excluding valet parking costs) for each month the spend target is not met.\n\n## Travel\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/du-credit-card/icons/travel-icons-01.svg?iar=0&hash=E7E827100166F77007C0A7FB031B3027)\n\nFree airport lounge access\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/du-credit-card/icons/travel-icons-02.svg?iar=0&hash=A6133FA38431875BF5D0DEE53445D19A)\n\nAirport fast track services\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/du-credit-card/icons/travel-icons-03.svg?iar=0&hash=47853D385C7F40932AC4CBFCA0CB4802)\n\nFree airport rides with Careem\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree airport lounge access\n\n\n\nGet free access to airport lounges globally, for you and a guest through Mastercard and DragonPass. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/168079/world-elite-mastercard-lounge-program-dp/0/4007/options/sortBy/popularity/category/1021/)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nAirport fast track services\n\n\n\n\n\n3 complimentary fast track services per year to skip the security queue across top airports in Europe, Turkey & Asia. Prebook using the priority service on the Travel Pass App. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/189142/airport-security-fast-track-services)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nFree airport rides with Careem\n\n\n\n\n\nUse the Careem app with your Mastercard to enjoy six airport transfers a year. (Does not include Hala Taxis). [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/195122/complimentary-airport-transfers-with-careem)\n\n\nOR\n\n## FAB Rewards\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/rewards-icon-1.svg?iar=0&hash=3125F24278D7C699076CD0D570E4FB8C)\n\nReceive up to 20 FAB Rewards on luxury spending\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/rewards-icon-2.svg?iar=0&hash=515DC9C8001CC60861DE68E17841BADE)\n\nGet 10 FAB Rewards on eco-friendly purchases\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/rewards-icon-3.svg?iar=0&hash=428DC57656B525ADC8BCA9478A800AFF)\n\nUp to 5 FAB Rewards on all other spending including abroad\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGet up to 20 FAB Rewards on luxury spending\n\n\n\n\n\nEarn 20 FAB Rewards at brands such as Hermes, Cartier, Harrods, Van Cleef, Prada, Gucci, Dior, Hugo Boss and more. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGet 10 FAB Rewards on eco-friendly purchases\n\n\n\n\n\nReceive 10 FAB Rewards for each  1 spent at eco-friendly merchants including Kibsons, Emirates Bio Farm, Just Vegan, The Giving Movement, BON organic perfumes and over 200 more brands in the UAE. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nGet up to 5 FAB Rewards on all other spending including abroad\n\n\n\n\n\nGet up to 5 FAB Rewards\\* for each  1 spent on all other spending in the UAE and abroad (including non-AED currencies). [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nUse your FAB Rewards for cashback and much more\n\n\n\n\n\nFAB Rewards is FAB’s exclusive loyalty programme which rewards you across your banking. Redeem Rewards on retail, dining, cashback, miles and entertainment. Manage your Rewards quickly and easily through the FAB Mobile app. [More info on FAB Rewards](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/rewards)\n\n\n\nFAB Rewards earning is capped at 500,000 FAB Rewards per month except earning on luxury spending which is capped at 200,000 FAB Rewards each month.\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Selected categories will only earn 0.5 FAB Rewards per  1 spent. See [FAB Rewards Terms and Conditions](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/fab-reward-programmes/fab-rewards-terms-and-conditions-en.pdf?view=1) for more information on categories.\n\n## Protection\n\nBenefits\n\nAdditional Information\n\nBenefits\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/protection-01.svg?iar=0&hash=D07821E5EE88E62069546EBD11BF14F2)\n\nCredit Shield\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/protection-02.svg?iar=0&hash=77DBF4056CE53CF4ED3F875E7FE3B061)\n\nTravel inconvenience insurance\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/protection-03.svg?iar=0&hash=BDB5D708D8EE1371E49E355AC8D343D8)\n\nTravel medical insurance\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nCredit Shield\n\n\n\n\n\nOpt for Credit Shield so your outstanding balance will be paid if something prevents you from making your card payments.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nTravel inconvenience insurance\n\n\n\n\n\nIf your luggage goes missing or you experience flight delays – you’re covered. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163159/travel-inconvenience-insurance-world-elite/0/4007/options/cardType/2/)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nTravel medical insurance\n\n\n\n\n\nGet medical care and emergency help while travelling in case you need it. Get up to USD 500,000 for you, your family and your helper. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163161/travel-medical-insurance/0/4007/options/cardType/2/)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nRental Collision and Loss Damage Waiver\n\n\n\n\n\nIn case of physical damage to a rental car or theft, you are covered up to USD 50,000. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163261/rental-collision-and-loss-damage-waiver-flex-product/0/4007/options/cardType/2/)\n\n\nOR\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/fab-elite-cc-onboarding.png?iar=0&hash=E7EFF72FE64189491FB946EBC443A8B3)\n\n## Apply now for a FAB Elite Credit Card\n\nReady to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.\n\nMinimum Monthly Salary\n\n **40,000**\n\nAnnual Fee\n\n **1,200**\n\n![Percentage Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/icon-percentage)\n\nReady to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.\n\n[Apply now](https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=CC38F05A-D90F-454F-9192-E2769B4FFE35&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=none&utm_keyword=not%20provided&utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Ffab-elite-credit-card&tst_id=null#apply-now \"\")\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/award/badge.jpg?h=1181&iar=0&w=1551&hash=8569A856DAFB32CC3432949B9864F9E1)\n\n## FAB has won “Best Achievement in Sustainability” at The Cards & Payments Awards – Middle East for our new FAB Elite Credit Card in partnership with MasterCard\n\nThe FAB Elite Credit Card is designed to empower our customers to integrate eco-conscious practices in their everyday lifestyle by rewarding them with:\n\n- Bonus FAB Rewards for spending at eco-friendly merchants\n- Tree planting programme linked to everyday spending\n- Engaging eco prizes with seasonal gamification features on the FAB Mobile App\n\n## How to easily apply for your credit card online\n\nWatch this short video and see how you can apply for a FAB credit card online in just a few minutes.\n\nHow to Apply Online for a FAB Credit Card\\_EN from First Abu Dhabi Bank on Vimeo\n\n![video thumbnail](https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/2007623580-1ac9340085989191c4046e707c893dba9ffecac73264f60c91c1147d38d981a0-d?mw=80&q=85)\n\nPlaying in picture-in-picture\n\nPlay\n\n00:00\n\n01:33\n\nSettings\n\nQualityAuto\n\nPicture-in-PictureFullscreen\n\n;\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/promotions/2025/mclaren-f1-cards-offer/10-card-pdp-promo-tile-mclaren-f1.jpg?h=832&iar=0&w=1024&hash=C9567B08FE8C6813EBAD068966F16FEA)\n\nAs the Official Race Partner of the McLaren F1 Team, FAB is bringing the thrill of the track to your wallet.\n\nFor a limited time, subscribe to our McLaren Racing Mastercard Pass and enjoy a McLaren F1 card design update, exclusive fan content, freebies, and a chance to win a trip to the McLaren Technology Centre in the UK.\n\n[Learn more\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/promotions/mclaren-f1-cards-offer \"\")\n\n## Make the most of your credit card with FAB's fantastic offers\n\n[See all offers\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers \"\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/the-green-planet/green-planet-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=F3E4C17F9CC3E76374BDD41CB9FEDB5D)\\\\\n\\\\\nThe Green Planet\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 20% discount on day-passes\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/the-green-planet-fab \"The Green Planet\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/dubai-parks-resorts/dpr-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=AEBB96520616EFC115D3ADA6A48ABD3F)\\\\\n\\\\\nDubai Parks and Resorts\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 20% discount on entry tickets\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/dubai-parks-resorts-fab \"Dubai Parks and Resorts\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/view-at-the-palm/theview-palm-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=E1A0AEF853EFBE036BFF51870CE83F24)\\\\\n\\\\\nThe View at the Palm\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n20% Discount on entry tickets\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/view-at-the-palm \"The View at the Palm\")\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/wild-wadi-waterpark/wild-wadi-352x198.jpg?h=198&iar=0&w=352&hash=9597F4570A7E6738792343EB01A0026C)\\\\\n\\\\\nWild Wadi Waterpark\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nUnlock special discounts on entry passes and more\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)September 15 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/wild-wadi-waterpark-fab \"Wild Wadi Waterpark\")\n\n[![Al Futtaim](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/alfuttaim_img.jpg?h=200&iar=0&w=300&hash=AC9CBB629C73A7617AFBA345ABDAF7C7)\\\\\n\\\\\nAl Futtaim\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n0% Easy Payment Plan at Al Futtaim brands\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/alfuttaimepp \"Al Futtaim\")\n\n## Beyond Benefits: Your card has you covered.\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg)![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/Basic-Icons_blue.svg)\n\nCredit Shield\n\nStay covered so your outstanding balance is paid if you're unable to make card payments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-shield)\n\nBalance Transfers\n\nTransfer high-interest card balances to FAB and you could get lower interest rates.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/balance-transfer)\n\nQuick Cash\n\nAccess fast cash with easy withdrawals right from your credit card.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/quick-cash)\n\nEasy Payment Plans\n\nGet easy instalment plans with competitive rates and flexible repayments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/easy-payment-plan)\n\nStanding Instructions for Recurring Payments\n\nEnjoy the convenience of automatic bill payments with our Standing Instructions facility for up to 20 bill payments.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-recurring-plans)\n\nStanding Instruction for a One Time Payment\n\nMake payments to over 75 partners including school fees, utility bills, insurance premiums, property maintenance fees and more.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-one-time-payments)\n\nCredit Card Bill Payments\n\nPay your credit card bills for FREE through any of our payment channels.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-card-bill-payment)\n\nWallet Shield\n\nCovers against fraudulent transactions on your lost or stolen credit cards, stolen cash and theft of identification or keys.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/wallet-shield)\n\nAccident Care Plan\n\nGet coverage of up to  150,000 to cater to any unforeseen eventualities.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/accident-care-plan)\n\nEnhanced Security for Online Purchases\n\nSafeguard the online transactions you make with your FAB credit card with a One-Time Password (OTP).\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/enhanced-security)\n\nUtility Bill Payments\n\nPay your bills through our convenient banking channels.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/utility-bill-payments)\n\nChip and PIN\n\nYour FAB credit card has an encrypted chip along with enhanced security using a Personal Identification Number (PIN).\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/chip-and-pin)\n\nPayment Partners\n\nTake a look at our extensive list of payment partners.\n\n[Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/payment-partners)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/forms/forms-en.jpg?h=900&iar=0&w=704&hash=A93D982D8E0977512DF592F8F85E8E96)\n\n## Request a Callback\n\n(Optional)\n\n(Optional)\n\n93/255\n\n(Optional)\n\n(Optional)\n\n0/255\n\n## Enter your details below\n\nWe will call you back within 24 hours to proceed with your inquiry. (\\*denotes mandatory fields)\n\nFirst Name \\*\n\nFirst Name \\*\n\n0/25\n\nLast Name \\*\n\nLast Name \\*\n\n0/25\n\nCompany name (Optional)\n\nCompany name (Optional)\n\nPhone Number \\*\n\nPhone Number \\*\n\n0/10\n\nEmail \\*\n\nEmail \\*\n\nEmirate \\*\n\nEmirate \\*\n\nNationality \\*\n\nNationality \\*\n\nSalary per month \\*\n\nSalary per month \\*\n\n##### Do you own a car?\n\nYes\n\nNo\n\n##### How much do you spend on utility bills per month?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\n##### How much do you spend on entertainment per month?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\n##### How many times do you travel per year?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\n##### How much do you spend on education per year?\n\n0![Slider Indicator Alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_slider-indicator.svg)\n\nAED\n\nI hereby authorise First Abu Dhabi Bank to obtain a credit information report on me from the AI Etihad Credit Bureau(or any successor organisation).\n\nI read and accept the **[Terms and Conditions](https://www.bankfab.com/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated)**.\n\nApply now\n\nreCAPTCHA\n\nRecaptcha requires verification.\n\nprotected by **reCAPTCHA**\n\n## Find out more about our Fees, Terms and Conditions.\n\n[Schedule of Fees\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-bl