lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free access to 60+ beach clubs, gyms and sports clubs with ADV+</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Enjoy free access to luxury beach clubs, gyms and sports centres across the UAE * Access is through the ADV+ app using a unique voucher code. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about free access through ADV+ app\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Up to 40% off at top restaurants in the UAE with ADV+</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Receive a discount of up to 40% for you and your friends at some of the top hotel restaurants across the UAE. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about discounts with top restaurants in the UAE\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Get dedicated lifestyle concierge support 24/7</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>If you would like assistance with travel planning, booking fine dining or access to exclusive events – call the 24/7 lifestyle concierge service to help you plan and book. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about lifestyle concierge support\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163202/world-elite-mastercard-concierge/0/4007/options/cardType/2/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Guaranteed gift of gold from the FAB Rewards Shop </div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Spend  500,000 a year or more on your card and you'll be rewarded with gold! To redeem just visit the FAB Rewards section on the FAB Mobile app and redeem your gold gift. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about FAB Rewards Shop\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Eco-friendly benefits and Rewards</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>For each new card, we’ll plant a tree on your behalf with Give a Ghaf. Plus, earn 10 FAB Rewards at eco-friendly merchants including Kibsons, Emirates Bio Farm, Just Vegan, The Giving Movement, BON organic perfumes and over 200 more brands in the UAE. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about welcome offer benefits\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-4 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><small>*Subject to an &nbsp;10,000 monthly spend on the card. Beach / sport access is chargeable at &nbsp;300 for each month the spend target is not met.</small></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"b0b7dbce-7117-44c2-963b-e3da25cc5f69\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_b0b7dbce-7117-44c2-963b-e3da25cc5f69\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">Lifestyle</h2><div class=\"group-tabs\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"tabs-carousel-wrapper tabs-component-pc\"><div id=\"tabs-car-control-prev-68578\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-left tabs-carousel-control-hidden\"><div></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal tabs-carousel swiper-backface-hidden\" role=\"tabli