bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Enjoy one-hour free valet parking at premium locations</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get a free hour of valet parking up to 5 times a month at premium UAE locations including Mall of the Emirates, City Walk, Dubai Mall, Yas Mall, Al Qana, Dubai Hills Mall and many more.* <a aria-label=\"Learn more about free hour of valet parking\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Buy one get one free movie ticket offer at Roxy Cinemas</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Plus, enjoy eight movie tickets from  20 each per month at Reel, Royal, Star, VOX Cinemas.* <a aria-label=\"Learn more about free movie ticket offer\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">20% off Emaar attractions</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>You can avail an unlimited discount of up to 20% at KidZania, Dubai Aquarium &amp; Underwater Zoo – Penguin Cove and Nursery Experience, The Storm Coaster and Zabeel Sports District. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about discounts on Emaar attractions” href=\" https:=\"\" www.bankfab.com=\"\" -=\"\" media=\"\" fab-uds=\"\" personal=\"\" credit-cards=\"\" fab-elite-credit-card=\"\" card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=\"1\" \"=\"\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">20% off Dubai Holding attractions</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>An up to 20% unlimited discount at Wild Wadi, Dubai Parks and Resorts, Inside Burj Al Arab, The Green Planet and The View Palm. \n<a aria-label=\"Learn more about discounts on Dubai Holding attractions\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">30% off golf worldwide with Mastercard Golf Programme</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>With Mastercard’s’ Golf Programme by Thriwe - you can get 30% off, or one free guest on your next game of golf at selected golf clubs worldwide. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about Mastercard Golf Programme\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/sports/product/194217/mastercard-golf-program-by-thriwe/0/4007/options/category/507/location/19588/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-4 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><small>*Subject to an &nbsp;10,000 monthly spend on the card. Cinema benefits / valet parking is chargeable at  100 (excluding valet parking costs) for each month the spend target is not met.</small></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"ff2f1b2f-9e89-417c-9f72-4c416aa4be5e\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_ff2f1b2f-9e89-417c-9f72-4c416aa4be5e\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">Travel</h2><div class=\"group-tabs\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"tabs-carousel-wrapper tabs-component-pc\"><div id=\"tabs-car-control-prev-31463\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-left tabs-carousel-control-hidden\"><div></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal tabs-carousel swiper-backface-hidden\" role=\"tablist\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"