c\">Get free access to airport lounges globally, for you and a guest through Mastercard and DragonPass. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about free airport lounge access\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/168079/world-elite-mastercard-lounge-program-dp/0/4007/options/sortBy/popularity/category/1021/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Airport fast track services</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>3 complimentary fast track services per year to skip the security queue across top airports in Europe, Turkey &amp; Asia. Prebook using the priority service on the Travel Pass App. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about airport fast track services\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/189142/airport-security-fast-track-services\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Free airport rides with Careem</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Use the Careem app with your Mastercard to enjoy six airport transfers a year. (Does not include Hala Taxis). <a aria-label=\"Learn more about free airport rides with Careem\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/195122/complimentary-airport-transfers-with-careem\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"c356bdab-1f81-4d09-a1fc-c6e7165be275\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_c356bdab-1f81-4d09-a1fc-c6e7165be275\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">FAB Rewards</h2><div class=\"group-tabs\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"tabs-carousel-wrapper tabs-component-pc\"><div id=\"tabs-car-control-prev-96491\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-left tabs-carousel-control-hidden\"><div></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal tabs-carousel swiper-backface-hidden\" role=\"tablist\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); transition-duration: 300ms;\"><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\" id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\"><button id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab tabs-carousel-tab-active\">Benefits</button></div><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\" id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\"><button id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab\">Additional Information</button></div></div><div class=\"swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-clickable swiper-pagination-bullets swiper-pagination-horizontal\"><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-active\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet\"></span></div></div><div id=\"tabs-car-control-next-96491\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-right\"><div></div></div></div><div class=\"Dropdown-root tabs-dropdown tabs-component-mobile\"><div class=\"Dropdown-control tabs-dropdown-label-wrapper\" aria-haspopup=\"listbox\"><div class=\"Dropdown-placeholder tabs-dropdown-label is-selected\">Benefits</div><div class=\"Dropdown-arrow-wrapper\"><div class=\"tabs-dropdown-arrow \"></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Benefits\" class=\"tab-item-container showing d-none\"><div class=\"columns-splitter add-margins\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/rewards-icon-1.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=3125F24278D7C699076CD0D570E4FB8C\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Receive up to 20 FAB Rewards on luxury spending</span></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/rewards-icon-2.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=515DC9C8001CC60861DE68E17841BADE\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Get 10 FAB Rewards on eco-friendly purchases</span></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/rewards-icon-3.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=428DC57656B525ADC8BCA9478A800AFF\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Up to 5 FAB Rewards on all other spending including abroad</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Additional_Information\" class=\"tab-item-container d-none d-none\"><div class=\"bullet-point-listing content remove-seperator\"><ul class=\"bpl-items hide-or-variation-one\"><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Get up to 20 FAB Rewards on luxury spending</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Earn 20 FAB Rewards at brands such as Hermes, Cartier, Harrods, Van Cleef, Prada, Gucci, Dior, Hugo Boss and more. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about FAB Rewards on luxury spending\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Get 10 FAB Rewards on eco-friendly purchases</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Receive 10 FAB Rewards for each &nbsp;1 spent at eco-friendly merchants including Kibsons, Emirates Bio Farm, Just Vegan, The Giving Movement, BON organic perfumes and over 200 more brands in the UAE. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about FAB Rewards on eco-friendly purchases\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Get up to 5 FAB Rewards on all other spending including abroad</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get up to 5 FAB Rewards* for each  1 spent on all other spending in the UAE and abroad (including non-AED currencies). <a aria-label=\"Learn more about FAB Rewards on all other spending\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/card-benefit-terms-and-conditions.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Use your FAB Rewards for cashback and much more</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>FAB Rewards is FAB’s exclusive loyalty programme which rewards you across your banking. Redeem Rewards on retail, dining, cashback, miles and entertainment. Manage your Rewards quickly and easily through the FAB Mobile app. <a href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/rewards\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">More info on FAB Rewards</a></p>\n<p>FAB Rewards earning is capped at 500,000 FAB Rewards per month except earning on luxury spending which is capped at 200,000 FAB Rewards each month.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-text\"><small>*Selected categories will only earn 0.5 FAB Rewards per &nbsp;1 spent. See <a href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated/fab-reward-programmes/fab-rewards-terms-and-conditions-en.pdf?view=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">FAB Rewards Terms and Conditions</a>&nbsp;for more information on categories.</small></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"770138e1-da2e-4990-b1d8-04eff9f9a86d\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_770138e1-da2e-4990-b1d8-04eff9f9a86d\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content tabs-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"invisible-anchor\"></div><h2 class=\"tabs-component-title\">Protection</h2><div class=\"group-tabs\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"tabs-carousel-wrapper tabs-component-pc\"><div id=\"tabs-car-control-prev-60274\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-left tabs-carousel-control-hidden\"><div></div></div><div class=\"swiper swiper-initialized swiper-horizontal tabs-carousel swiper-backface-hidden\" role=\"tablist\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); transition-duration: 300ms;\"><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-active\" id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\"><button id=\"tab_Benefits\" aria-controls=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-selected=\"true\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab tabs-carousel-tab-active\">Benefits</button></div><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\" id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\"><button id=\"tab_Additional_Information\" aria-controls=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-selected=\"false\" role=\"tab\" class=\"tabs-carousel-tab\">Additional Information</button></div></div><div class=\"swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-clickable swiper-pagination-bullets swiper-pagination-horizontal\"><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-active\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet\"></span></div></div><div id=\"tabs-car-control-next-60274\" class=\"tabs-carousel-control tabs-carousel-control-right\"><div></div></div></div><div class=\"Dropdown-root tabs-dropdown tabs-component-mobile\"><div class=\"Dropdown-control tabs-dropdown-label-wrapper\" aria-haspopup=\"listbox\"><div class=\"Dropdown-placeholder tabs-dropdown-label is-selected\">Benefits</div><div class=\"Dropdown-arrow-wrapper\"><div class=\"tabs-dropdown-arrow \"></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Benefits\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Benefits\" class=\"tab-item-container showing d-none\"><div class=\"columns-splitter add-margins\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/protection-01.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=D07821E5EE88E62069546EBD11BF14F2\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Credit Shield</span></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/protection-02.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=77DBF4056CE53CF4ED3F875E7FE3B061\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Travel inconvenience insurance</span></div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 col-xl-4\"><div class=\"listing-with-icon-and-text add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"lwiat-item\"><div class=\"lwiat-item-icon-wrapper\"><img class=\"lwiat-item-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/icons/protection-03.svg?iar=0&amp;hash=BDB5D708D8EE1371E49E355AC8D343D8\"></div><span class=\"lwiat-item-desc\">Travel medical insurance</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div role=\"tabpanel\" data-e2e-class=\"styleguide-layout-tabs-tab\" id=\"panel_Additional_Information\" aria-labelledby=\"tab_Additional_Information\" class=\"tab-item-container d-none d-none\"><div class=\"bullet-point-listing content remove-seperator\"><ul class=\"bpl-items hide-or-variation-one\"><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Credit Shield</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Opt for Credit Shield so your outstanding balance will be paid if something prevents you from making your card payments.</p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-0\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Travel inconvenience insurance</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>If your luggage goes missing or you experience flight delays – you’re covered. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about travel inconvenience insurance\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163159/travel-inconvenience-insurance-world-elite/0/4007/options/cardType/2/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-1\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Travel medical insurance</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>Get medical care and emergency help while travelling in case you need it. Get up to USD 500,000 for you, your family and your helper. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about travel medical insurance\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163161/travel-medical-insurance/0/4007/options/cardType/2/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-2\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span><li class=\"bpl-item bpl-item-1 bpl-item-or\"><div class=\"bpl-item-icon\"><span class=\"icon-svg-content\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg\" alt=\"icon.node-minus.alt\" loading=\"lazy\"></span></div><div class=\"bpl-item-content\"><div class=\"bpl-item-content-title\">Rental Collision and Loss Damage Waiver</div><div class=\"global-rich-text bpl-item-content-desc\"><p>In case of physical damage to a rental car or theft, you are covered up to USD 50,000. <a aria-label=\"Learn more about Rental Collision and Loss Damage Waiver\" href=\"https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/163261/rental-collision-and-loss-damage-waiver-flex-product/0/4007/options/cardType/2/\" target=\"_blank\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></li><span class=\"bpl-items-separator separator-1 separator-3 d-none\"><div class=\"bpl-items-separator-text\">OR</div></span></ul></div></div></div></div></section></div></section><section id=\"3797cf8d-048a-4166-ad5d-82e1b9f88af3\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_3797cf8d-048a-4166-ad5d-82e1b9f88af3\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content content-component add-margins margin-bottom-0 margin-top-40\"></div></section><section id=\"get-your-card\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_get-your-card\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"cards-list-component add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-cards-wrapper content\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card-sub\"><div class=\"cards-list-list-card-content\"><div class=\"cllc-left\"><div class=\"cl-card-header\"><div class=\"cl-card-header-image-wrapper\"><img class=\"cl-card-header-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/fab-elite-cc-onboarding.png?iar=0&amp;hash=E7EFF72FE64189491FB946EBC443A8B3\"></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-footer cllc-footer-pc without-padding\"></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-description cllc-right\"><h2 class=\"cl-card-desc-title\">Apply now for a FAB Elite Credit Card </h2><div class=\"global-rich-text cl-card-desc-text\"><p>Ready to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.</p></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-features\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature\"><p class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-title\">Minimum Monthly Salary</p><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-value\"> <b>40,000</b></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature\"><p class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-title\">Annual Fee</p><div class=\"cl-card-desc-feature-value\"> <b>1,200</b></div></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-wrapper\"><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-icon\"><img src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/icon-percentage\" alt=\"Percentage Alt\" title=\"icon.percentage.title\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"cl-card-desc-offer-text\">Ready to enjoy the benefits of your credit card? Start your online application today.</div></div></div><div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;\"><a data-isonboarding=\"true\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-button-type=\"type_a\" id=\"930e3a42-ab0b-45b4-9be5-a066a748d191\" field=\"[object Object]\" href=\"https://apply.bankfab.com/en-ae/?card=CC38F05A-D90F-454F-9192-E2769B4FFE35&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_keyword=not%20provided&amp;utm_landing_page=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bankfab.com%2Fen-ae%2Fpersonal%2Fcredit-cards%2Ffab-elite-credit-card&amp;tst_id=null#apply-now\" class=\"button ev_1 button-text-simple-children button-contained-primary\" datalayertext=\"Apply now\" aria-label=\"Apply now for FAB Elite Credit Card\" title=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" data-text=\"\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\" style=\"display: inline-block; max-width: 126px; width: 100%; text-align: center; margin: 0px;\"><div>Apply now</div></a></div></div></div><div class=\"cl-card-footer cllc-footer-mobile without-padding\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"1aa36f43-a754-4cf1-a743-d657255b71fc\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_1aa36f43-a754-4cf1-a743-d657255b71fc\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content left-aligned add-margins margin-top-60\"><div class=\"cards-listing-card\"><div class=\"cl-card-image-wrapper\"><img class=\"cl-card-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-elite-credit-card/award/badge.jpg?h=1181&amp;iar=0&amp;w=1551&amp;hash=8569A856DAFB32CC3432949B9864F9E1\"></div><div class=\"cl-card-content\"><h2 class=\"cl-card-content-title\">FAB has won “Best Achievement in Sustainability” at The Cards &amp; Payments Awards – Middle East for our new FAB Elite Credit Card in partnership with MasterCard</h2><div class=\"global-rich-text cl-card-content-desc\"><br><p>The FAB Elite Credit Card is designed to empower our customers to integrate eco-conscious practices in their everyday lifestyle by rewarding them with:</p></div><div class=\"global-rich-text cl-card-content-content\"><ul>\n<li>Bonus FAB Rewards for spending at eco-friendly merchants</li>\n<li>Tree planting programme linked to everyday spending</li>\n<li>Engaging eco prizes with seasonal gamification features on the FAB Mobile App</li>\n</ul></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"how-to-video\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_how-to-video\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content add-margins margin-top-60\"><section id=\"0223f675-4df9-4efc-ae37-2039b63dc3a2\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_0223f675-4df9-4efc-ae37-2039b63dc3a2\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"columns-splitter add-margins\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-6 col-xl-6\"><div class=\"content content-component add-margins margin-bottom-20 margin-top-20\"><div class=\"global-rich-text description\"><h2 class=\"header3\">How to easily apply for your credit card online</h2>\n<p>Watch this short video and see how you can apply for a FAB  credit card online in just a few minutes.</p>\n\n</div></div></div><div class=\"columns-splitter-column col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-5 col-lg-6 col-xl-6\"><div class=\"video-component content add-margins margin-bottom-0 margin-top-0\"><div class=\"fullscreen\"><div style=\"width: 640px; height: 360px;\"><div data-vimeo-initialized=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden;\"><div src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1077222312?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"426\" height=\"240\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" title=\"How to Apply Online for a FAB Credit Card_EN\" data-ready=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" data-original-tag=\"iframe\">\n  \n  \n  \n  <l