452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-1\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Credit Shield</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Stay covered so your outstanding balance is paid if you're unable to make card payments.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-shield\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide-next\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-2\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Balance Transfers</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Transfer high-interest card balances to FAB and you could get lower interest rates.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/balance-transfer\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Quick Cash</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Access fast cash with easy withdrawals right from your credit card.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/quick-cash\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-4\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Easy Payment Plans</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Get easy instalment plans with competitive rates and flexible repayments.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/easy-payment-plan\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-5\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Standing Instructions for Recurring Payments</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Enjoy the convenience of automatic bill payments with our Standing Instructions facility for up to 20 bill payments. </p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-recurring-plans\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-6\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Standing Instruction for a One Time Payment </span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Make payments to over 75 partners including school fees, utility bills, insurance premiums, property maintenance fees and more.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/si-for-one-time-payments\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-1\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Credit Card Bill Payments</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Pay your credit card bills for FREE through any of our payment channels.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/credit-card-bill-payment\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Wallet Shield</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Covers against fraudulent transactions on your lost or stolen credit cards, stolen cash and theft of identification or keys.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/wallet-shield\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-2\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Accident Care Plan</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Get coverage of up to  150,000 to cater to any unforeseen eventualities.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/accident-care-plan\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-3\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Enhanced Security for Online Purchases</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Safeguard the online transactions you make with your FAB credit card with a One-Time Password (OTP).</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/enhanced-security\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-1\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Utility Bill Payments</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Pay your bills through our convenient banking channels.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/utility-bill-payments\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-4\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Chip and PIN</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Your FAB credit card has an encrypted chip along with enhanced security using a Personal Identification Number (PIN).</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/chip-and-pin\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"width: 452px; margin-right: 32px;\"><div class=\"carousel-informative-slide ci-slide-1\"><div class=\"ci-slide-image-wrapper\"></div><span class=\"ci-slide-heading\">Payment Partners</span><div class=\"global-rich-text ci-slide-text\"><p>Take a look at our extensive list of payment partners.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color:#fff !important; \" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/services/payment-partners\" data-aquried=\"true\" data-shouldattachevent=\"true\" data-pre-attach=\"true\">Learn more</a></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-clickable swiper-pagination-bullets swiper-pagination-horizontal\"><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light carousel-bullet-active\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span><span class=\"carousel-bullet carousel-bullet-light\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"ade0b03c-e6b1-40dd-875a-52e4a160006c\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_ade0b03c-e6b1-40dd-875a-52e4a160006c\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"content add-margins margin-top-60\"><section id=\"apply-now\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div id=\"component_apply-now\" class=\"fake-anchor\"></div><div class=\"eligibility-message add-margins %7bE93DF388-1473-421C-9A90-D73B3CE1E17B%7d%7c%7bD61B2328-C6A3-4EDD-8BF7-FC8864024ED1%7d%c2%a2eredAlignmentRight\"><div class=\"panel left content-left\"><div class=\"image-layer\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/forms/forms-en.jpg?h=900&amp;iar=0&amp;w=704&amp;hash=A93D982D8E0977512DF592F8F85E8E96\"></div><div class=\"wrap-data\"><div class=\"wrap flex-it flex-align-item-center flex-justify-center\"><div class=\"auto\"><h2 class=\"global-rich-text description\">Request a Callback</h2></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel ri