          "markdown": "[Skip to content](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/fab-world-elite#main-content-section)\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n- English\n\nEnglish\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  - [العربية\\\\\n    \\\\\n    العربية](https://www.bankfab.com/ar-ae/personal/credit-cards/fab-world-elite)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n[![Branch locator](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/location.svg?iar=0&hash=BE0DB30E697196E30449E6F9E2217AA9)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/branch-locator \"\")[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/phone.svg?iar=0&hash=9081683D4B6CA5EF886D8EC61792E421)Customer Care](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/contact-us \"\")![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)Login\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)\n\n## Login\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\nPersonal Banking\n\n- [Personal Online Banking (UAE)](https://online.bankfab.com/PersonalBankingWeb/login)\n- [Ratibi Prepaid Card Balance Enquiry](https://ppc.magnati.com/ppc-inquiry)\n\nCorporate & Investment\n\n- [FAB Business Portal](https://business.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABeAccess - Corporate Online Banking](https://fabeaccess.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABOnline Banking Cash (Corporate)](https://online.bankfab.com/fabonline)\n- [FABOnline Banking Trade (Corporate)](https://fabeaccesstrade.bankfab.com/fabonlinetrade/portal)\n- [iBanking Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking.bankfab.com/iportalweb/)\n- [IPO/RI Subscription](https://www.bankfab.com/v1/en-ae/investment-banking/iposubscription)\n- [FAB Securities Services (INSIGHT)](https://fss.bankfab.com/)\n- [iBanking ADGM Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking-adgm.bankfab.com/iportalweb)\n\nFAB Securities\n\n- [FABS Online](https://www.securitiesfab.com/EInvest)\n- [FABS Research Portal](https://fabsresearch.bankfab.com/Researchportal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)Login\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/lock.svg?iar=0&hash=1C5FF158DEB5328BE913CA03CA29CEA5)\n\n## Login\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\nPersonal Banking\n\n- [Personal Online Banking (UAE)](https://online.bankfab.com/PersonalBankingWeb/login)\n- [Ratibi Prepaid Card Balance Enquiry](https://ppc.magnati.com/ppc-inquiry)\n\nCorporate & Investment\n\n- [FAB Business Portal](https://business.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABeAccess - Corporate Online Banking](https://fabeaccess.bankfab.com/)\n- [FABOnline Banking Cash (Corporate)](https://online.bankfab.com/fabonline)\n- [FABOnline Banking Trade (Corporate)](https://fabeaccesstrade.bankfab.com/fabonlinetrade/portal)\n- [iBanking Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking.bankfab.com/iportalweb/)\n- [IPO/RI Subscription](https://www.bankfab.com/v1/en-ae/investment-banking/iposubscription)\n- [FAB Securities Services (INSIGHT)](https://fss.bankfab.com/)\n- [iBanking ADGM Corporate Online Banking](https://ibanking-adgm.bankfab.com/iportalweb)\n\nFAB Securities\n\n- [FABS Online](https://www.securitiesfab.com/EInvest)\n- [FABS Research Portal](https://fabsresearch.bankfab.com/Researchportal)\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg?iar=0&hash=654DA36F2A1CE0EE98E79136FCE3C7FC)\n\n![icon.close_white.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_close-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon_burger-white.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/icons/icon-close-white)\n\n[Personal](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal)\n\n[Business](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/business-banking)\n\n[Corporate](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/corporate-banking)\n\n[Investment Banking](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/investment-banking)\n\n[Islamic](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/islamic-banking)\n\n[Private](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/private)\n\n[About FAB](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/about-fab)\n\n[Subsidiaries](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/subsidiaries)\n\n[Insights](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/insights)\n\nInternational\n\n[![FAB home page](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/data/media/img/fab-logo.svg?iar=0&hash=A347BC84EEF1BA82ED1A74E455D9E992)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal \"First Abu Dhabi Bank home page\")\n\n![Search](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/search.svg)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-world-elite/elite-world-banner-en.jpg?h=608&iar=0&w=1440&hash=E51253F8DDD2B88070CB408AFCE22301)\n\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-world-elite/fab-world-elite.png?h=327&iar=0&w=466&hash=7BEB46F47D21ECAD47B3BDCB6E7E991C)\n\n# FAB World Elite Credit Card\n\n- 24/7 concierge service\n- Worldwide airport lounge access for you and a guest\n- Travel insurance coverage of up to USD 500,000\n\nExclusive to Private Banking Customers. Applications are by invitation only.\n\n## WARNING\n\n- If you make only the minimum repayment/payment each period, you will pay more in interest/profit/fees and it will take you longer to pay off your outstanding balance.\n\nLifestyle Benefits\n\nTravel Benefits\n\nProtection Benefits\n\nLifestyle Benefits\n\n## Take your lifestyle global\n\nDiscover an exclusive range of privileges to enjoy life’s luxuries\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nValet Parking\n\n\n\n\n\nA convenient solution for all those enjoy the basic luxuries in life! FAB World Elite Credit Cardholders can enjoy 4 valet parking services per month at select locations. [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nMovie tickets from just AED 15\n\n\n\n\n\nA great offering for all movie buffs! FAB World Elite Credit Cardholders can enjoy 8 movie tickets per month at AED 15 during weekdays and AED 20 during weekends with [Reel Cinemas, Cine Royal and](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated) [Oscar Cinema](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated) and at AED 20 during weekends at [VOX Cinemas](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\n24/7 Concierge Service\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nMake the most of your trip with a 24-hour Concierge Service to help you with an array of travel-related tasks. Please call [8000-444-8108](tel:80004448108) or [+1-312-843-5353](tel:0013128435353) to take advantage of this service.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nUBER Chauffeur Service\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nGet 20% off when you book a ride with Uber. Choose your preferred car type for immediate pick up or schedule for later. [Learn more](https://www.priceless.com/benefits-mea).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nDiscount on shipping using MyUS\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nShop at over 100,000 U.S. retailers, including Apple, Amazon and Ralph Lauren and get fast, reliable, affordable international shipping with MyUS, #1 in the industry with over 10 million packages shipped since 1997. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/lifestyle.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nEuropean Shopping Villages Offers\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nThe Bicester Village Shopping Collection is defined by its luxury brands, charming open-air ‘village’ settings, a welcoming and superior service, a calendar of events and, not least, exceptional value for money. World-leading brands offer savings of up to 60%, and sometimes more, on the recommended retail price, in their own luxuriously appointed boutiques, all year round. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/lifestyle.html).\n\n\nOR\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nBuy 1 Get 1 Free Offers\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nDownload the Mastercard Buy 1 Get 1 App to browse the best offers with 900+ offers across 90+ destinations and 600+ merchants. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/lifestyle.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nMastercard Offers\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nPlus hundreds more top-class offers available to FAB World Elite Credit Cardholders. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers.html).\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [www.mastercard.ae/worldelite](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers.html) for the latest updates.\n\n## Experience a better way to travel\n\nSit back and relax with the highest levels of service and comfort\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nAirport Transfers\n\n\n\n\n\nReaching the airport on time has never been easier! FAB World Elite Credit Cardholders can enjoy 8 complimentary airport transfers per annum. To book this service, please email [Fabtransfers@enatravels.com](mailto:Fabtransfers@enatravels.com) or call [04 852 4856](tel:048524856). [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nMeet and Greet Service\n\n\n\n\n\nGet welcomed at the airport in style! FAB World Elite Credit Cardholders can enjoy 8 complimentary Meet and Greet services per annum. To book this service, please call FAB Call Centre on [800 40000](tel:800 40000) or send completed booking form to [Meetandgreet@bankfab.com](mailto:Meetandgreet@bankfab.com). [Learn more](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated).\n\n\n\nNote: The service at Abu Dhabi airport is temporarily on hold until further notice.\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nAirport Lounge Access\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nTravel in style with access to more than 1,200 airport lounges worldwide for you and a guest. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/lounge-world-elite.html).\n\n\naria-label=\"Learn more about Airport Lounge Access\"\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nLuxury Serviced Apartment Discounts\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy a quality stay that includes a 10% discount, complimentary daily house cleaning on stays over 7 nights, at 2,000 onefinestay properties across London, Paris, Milan, Florence, Rome, New York, Los Angeles, San Francisco and Sydney. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nComplimentary nights at participating Marriott Bonvoy™ hotels\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nGet complimentary nights at over 200 participating Marriott Bonvoy™ hotels across the Middle East and Africa. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nDiscovery black-level membership from global hotel alliance\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nAs a World Elite Mastercard cardholder, be instantly upgraded to DISCOVERY Black-level membership, a loyalty programme of Global Hotel Alliance. Revel in the comfort of DISCOVERY across more than 550 hotels, including Anantara, Corinthia, Kempinski, and Pan Pacific Hotels and Resorts. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nLuxury serviced apartments and hotel offers\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nEnjoy the stunning views of the Indian Ocean from the Maldivian paradise or visit the Thailand resort, just one hour’s flight from Bangkok by private plane, that offers an unrivalled combination of luxury, environmentally friendly design and unforgettable, authentic Thai experiences. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nHertz Gold Plus Rewards® President's Circle Membership\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nRenting a car is now hassle-free. With World Elite Mastercard, you are automatically eligible for Hertz Gold Plus Rewards® President's Circle, which is otherwise obtainable through 20 qualifying Hertz Gold Plus Rewards® rentals in a 12-month period. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nMastercard® Airport Concierge\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nWhether you're departing, arriving, or just connecting flights, Mastercard Airport Concierge gives you access to a personalised meet and greet service, facilitating your airport experience. Enjoy a special saving of 15% on this VIP service at over 470 airports, globally. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nCleartrip Discount\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nGoing on a holiday or booking that business trip? Book your ticket on Cleartrip using your World Elite Mastercard and enjoy a 10% discount on any international roundtrip airfare. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nBook with Avis and receive exclusive offers\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nWhether you are traveling with your family or on a business trip, enjoy exclusive benefits with Avis. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/travel.html).\n\n\nOR\n\nEligible cardholders should call on [04-8524856](tel:048524856) and book the service at least 2 working days prior to their travel/ required drop-off or pick-up date. This desk would be available 6 days a week (Monday to Saturday) between 9am to 7pm.\n\n\\*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [www.mastercard.ae/worldelite](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers.html) for the latest updates.\n\n## We’ve got you and your purchases covered\n\nBuy with confidence using your FAB World Elite Credit Card thanks to our range of protection benefits\n\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nTravel accident insurance\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nYou and your loved ones deserve peace of mind every time you travel. Rest assured that you will receive compensation for medical care or emergency help if you need it for up to USD 500,000. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/insurance.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nRental collision and loss damage waiver\\*\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nSometimes accidents happen, whether or not they are your fault. With Rental Collision & Loss Damage Waiver, World Elite Mastercard® cardholders have insurance on rental vehicles for up to USD 50,000. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/insurance.html).\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nTravel inconvenience insurance\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nWhether your luggage goes amiss or flight delays interrupt your plans, World Elite Mastercard® can compensate you for up to USD 7,500. [Learn more.](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/insurance.html)\n\n\nOR\n- ![icon.node-minus.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/Fab2/data/media/svgs/icons/node-minus.svg)\n\n\n\nTravel insurance confirmation letter\\*\n\n\n\n\n\nAs a World Elite Mastercard® cardholder you can generate a letter online seamlessly and immediately for your Schengen or other visa requirements. [Learn more](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers/find-card-products/world-elite/insurance.html).\n\n\nOR\n\n\\*Service offered and supported by Mastercard. Terms and conditions of the offer(s) may change without prior notice. Visit [www.mastercard.ae/worldelite](https://www.mastercard.ae/en-ae/consumers.html) for the latest updates.\n\n[![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/filetype-pdf.svg?iar=0&hash=22FC3B81B68E327B6438F6FE0AD73487)![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/filetype-download.svg?iar=0&hash=E21B4FDE0129ED897E12731B2A9D3EB2)\\\\\n\\\\\nSchedule of fees and charges\\\\\n\\\\\nPDF](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/personal/credit-cards/fab-world-elite/fab-generic-soc.pdf) [![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/filetype-link.svg?iar=0&hash=46E1BF01B43335F04A153E0378B673EA)![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/filetype-link-hover.svg?iar=0&hash=DF9971E859E585FC578B407F48A3970D)\\\\\n\\\\\nCredit card terms and conditions](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/terms-and-conditions-consolidated)\n\n## Make the most of your credit card with FAB's fantastic offers\n\n[See all offers\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-blue.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-white.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-red.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.button-arrow-blue.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/button-arrow-black.svg)](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers \"\")\n\n[![Al Futtaim](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/alfuttaim_img.jpg?h=200&iar=0&w=300&hash=AC9CBB629C73A7617AFBA345ABDAF7C7)\\\\\n\\\\\nAl Futtaim\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\n0% Easy Payment Plan at Al Futtaim brands\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/alfuttaimepp \"Al Futtaim\")\n\n[![Amazon.ae](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/amazon-logo.jpg?h=200&iar=0&w=300&hash=FA91B0847100390DCE23B878334FBFF8)\\\\\n\\\\\nAmazon.ae\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy Interest Free Plan on Amazon.ae\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/amazon-epp-offer-2022 \"Amazon.ae\")\n\n[![Navrang Jewellers](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/navrang-jewellers_logo.jpg?h=200&iar=0&w=300&hash=539EEBA129C3FAFD980A3F917A0B2CEF)\\\\\n\\\\\nNavrang Jewellers\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nEnjoy a 0% Easy Payment Plan at Navrang Jewellers\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/navrang-jewellers-epp-offer \"Navrang Jewellers\")\n\n[![Carrefour](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/project/fab2/fab2/home/personal/offers/merchants/c4-evoucher.jpg?h=300&iar=0&w=600&hash=5CD9E9A2598EE4BE361A666084864481)\\\\\n\\\\\nCarrefour\\\\\n\\\\\n![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/ico-division.svg)\\\\\nAvail 0% installment plan for 3 and 6 months on your purchases\\\\\n\\\\\n![icon.clock.alt](https://www.bankfab.com/-/jssmedia/Project/FAB2/shared/images/icon-clock.svg)December 31 2026](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/credit-cards/offers/carrefour \"Carrefour\")\n\n## Need more help? Get in touch.\n\nContact us anytime for further assistance or check out our [FAQ page](https://www.bankfab.com/en-ae/personal/help-and-support/faqs) for more information.\n\n| For customers within the UAE | For customers outside of the UAE |\n| --- | --- |\n| ![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg) | [600 52 5500](tel:600525500) | ![](https://www.bankfab.com/-/media/fab-uds/common-images/icons/about-phone.svg) | [+971 2 681 1511](tel:009712681151) |\n\n![](https://page-source.com/resizeimage.ashx?ig=www.bankfab.com&sz=11444)",
